    "voice_pack_aicheck_note": "Buri gice kirungikwa kuri Gemini kugira gisuzumwe.",
    "voice_pack_intro_student": "Umunyeshure yandika buri jwi mu jwi ryiwe bwite (ni vyiza ku kwiyumva ko ari uwawe n'ukumenyereza ukuvuga). Kanda 👂 kugira wumve akarorero imbere, uhereze 🎙️ kugira wandike. Ijwi ry'umunyeshure ni icegeranyo kibanga: risigara kuri iki gikoresho, kandi \"Kurungika\" rikora dosiye IBANGA ucungera.",
    "voice_pack_intro": "Andika buri jwi mu jwi ryawe bwite: kanda 👂 kugira wumve akarorero, uhereze 🎙️ uvuge ijwi mu majambo make (\"/p/\", si \"pe\"). Porogaramu icuranga ijwi ryawe mu gihe co kuvanga, gutandukanya n'ikarata y'ishingiro. Amajwi atagira ico abikamwo abika ijwi risanzwe.",
    "voice_pack_consent_title": "Kwandika ijwi ry'umunyeshure",
    "voice_pack_consent_body": "Kwandika ijwi ry'umunyeshure ni icegeranyo kibanga gifise imiterere isa na biyometiriki. Risigara kuri iki gikoresho, iki gikoresho ntikirishira kuri internet na rimwe (isuzuma rya AI, niba urikoresheje, ni co kintu conyene kirungika igice hanze), kandi urashobora kurifuta igihe ico ari co cose. Emeza ko ufise uruhusha rwo kwandika uyu munyeshure.",
