    "voice_pack_tab_progress": "Iterambere",
    "voice_pack_progress_empty": "Andika amajwi (ukoresheje isuzuma ryawe 😀 / 🤔, canke Umumenyereza wa AI 🎯 uguruye) kugira wubake icegeranyo c'imyimenyerezo ng'aha. Buri kwandika kurandikwa kugira ubone ijwi ritera imbere uko igihe kirengana.",
    "voice_pack_progress_legend": "Icegeranyo c'imyimenyerezo, si ikibazo: buri kadomo ni ukwandika kumwe, kuva ku kera gushika ku gishasha. Icatsi = vyumvikanye neza (umunyeshure canke Umumenyereza wa AI), umuhondo-utukura = bandanya kwimenyereza, ikijuju = ntirasuzumwa.",
