      "multiply_fractions": "Gwiza ibice",
      "exit_ticket_generator": "🎫 Umukozi w'itike yo gusohoka",
      "generate_a_3_question_exit_ticket_on_t": "Kora itike yo gusohoka y'ibibazo 3 ku ngingo iheruka kwigishwa. Capura hanyuma utange ku iherezo ry'isomo.",
      "topic_2": "Ingingo",
      "generate_and_print_exit_ticket": "🖨 Kora kandi ucapure itike yo gusohoka",
      "grade_3_fraction_assessment_checklist": "Urutonde rwo Kugenzura Isuzuma ry'Igice ry'Umwaka wa 3",
      "grade_4_fraction_assessment_checklist": "Urutonde rwo Kugenzura Isuzuma ry'Igice ry'Umwaka wa 4",
      "grade_5_fraction_assessment_checklist": "Urutonde rwo Kugenzura Isuzuma ry'Igice ry'Umwaka wa 5",
      "assessment_checklist": "☑ Urutonde rwo kugenzura isuzuma",
      "per_grade_skills_checklists_use_during": "Inzandiko z'ubuhinga za buri mwaka. Koresha mu gihe c'isuzuma umuntu-ku-muntu canke gutegura inyigisho.",
      "my_child_says_i_hate_fractions": "Umwana wanje avuga \"Ndanka ibice\"",
      "very_common_fractions_break_the_rules_": "Bisanzwe cane. Ibice vyica amategeko abanyeshure biga ku biharuro vyuzuye — ibiharuro binini ntibisobanura buri gihe agaciro kanini. Uburake ni ubw'ukuri kandi bisanzwe. Fasha na: (1) gukoresha ivyitegererezo biboneka nka pizza canke imikanda y'igice, (2) guhuza n'ubuzima nyakuri (guteka, igihe, amahera), (3) kwimenyereza gato kandi kenshi (iminota 5 ku musi) aho kuba session ndende, (4) gushimira inguvu, atari inyishu nziza gusa.",
      "my_child_doesn_t_understand_why_proced": "Umwana wanje ntatahura IGITUMA uburyo bukora",
      "they_are_not_alone_most_students_learn": "Ntabwo ari bonyene — abanyeshure benshi biga uburyo imbere n'igituma inyuma. Fasha ukoresheje kuguma werekana ukuntu uburyo busa n'ishusho. \"Gwiza 3/4 na 1/2\" bishobora gushushanywa nk'urukiramende. Tab ya Op Proofs iyikubikorera. Baza \"kubera iki?\" mu bugwaneza kandi kenshi.",
      "how_can_i_help_with_homework_without_d": "Nshobora gute gufasha mu masomo yo mu rugo ntabikoreye?",
      "use_the_worked_examples_tab_they_show_": "Koresha tab ya Worked Examples — yerekana uburyo intambwe ku yindi bufise igituma. Nyura mu bibazo bisa hamwe, atari kimwe. Nimba bavuga \"Sinzi uko natangura,\" baza \"Ni iki ikibazo gisaba ko urondera? Ni iki tuzi?\" Sisitemu y'ibimenyetso mu Bibazo vy'Amajambo itanga ibimenyetso vy'urwego — gerageza ica mbere imbere y'inyishu.",
      "what_should_i_drill": "Ni iki nkwiye kwimenyereza?",
      "ies_practice_guide_recommends_1_magnit": "IES Practice Guide isaba: (1) iciyumviro c'ubunini (imirimo y'umurongo w'ibiharuro), (2) isano hagati y'ikiboneka n'ikimenyetso, (3) ibibazo vy'amajambo mu rwego. IRINDA: kwimenyereza ku buryo utatahura. Mara iminota 5 kuri Benchmark Trainer, 5 ku Bibazo vy'Amajambo, na 5 ku mukino — iyo ni session y'iminota 15 nziza.",
      "my_child_gets_the_procedure_right_but_": "Umwana wanje akora uburyo neza ariko inyishu mbi",
      "usually_means_a_small_arithmetic_error": "Akenshi bisigura ikosa rito ry'imibare (akr., yagwije nabi) canke ntiyaworoteje. Erekana Cheat Sheet — bashobora kugenzura akazi kabo intambwe ku yindi. Bashishikarize kwemeza n'uburyo butandukanye (bakebe imbere, canke bakoreshe icitegererezo gitandukanye).",
      "what_if_i_don_t_remember_fractions_wel": "Vyogenda gute nimba jewe ubwanje ntibuka ibice neza?",
      "you_don_t_have_to_be_the_expert_use_th": "Ntutegerezwa kuba incabwenge! Koresha Tab Guide na Worked Examples — bisigura uburyo neza. Iciza: erekana \"reka tubimenye hamwe.\" Ushobora kwiga hamwe n'umwana wawe. Tab y'Amajambo ifise akamaro no ku bantu bakuru.",
      "how_do_i_know_if_my_child_is_on_track": "Nzomenya gute nimba umwana wanje ari ku nzira?",
      "look_at_the_standards_tab_to_see_which": "Raba tab ya Standards kugira ngo urabe amahame ya CCSS bakwiye kumenya ku mwaka wabo. Tab ya Mastery yerekana iterambere. Ku kugenzura kwihuta: bashobora (a) gushushanya icitegererezo ca 3/4, (b) kuvuga igice kingana na 1/2, (c) kugereranya 2/3 na 3/4 no gusigura? Izo test zitatu zikubiyemwo ivyitezwe vyinshi vy'igice vya K-5.",
      "parent_guide": "👨‍👩‍👧 Ubuyobozi bw'abavyeyi",
      "guidance_for_parents_helping_kids_with": "Ubuyobozi ku bavyeyi bafasha abana ku bice mu rugo. Ingorane zisanzwe, impanuro zifatika, n'ico wobaza.",
      "the_why_of_learning_recruiting_interes": "\"IGITUMA\" c'ukwiga — gukwega ishaka, kubandanya inguvu, kwiyobora",
      "the_what_of_learning_perception_langua": "\"ICO\" ukwiga — kwumva, ururimi, ugutahura",
      "the_how_of_learning_physical_action_ex": "\"UKUNTU\" ukwiga — igikorwa c'umubiri, kwerekana, umurimo w'ubuyobozi",
      "udl_alignment_cast_guidelines": "🎨 Ihuza rya UDL — amabwirizwa ya CAST",
      "every_fraction_lab_feature_mapped_to_a": "Buri kiranga ca Fraction Lab kihujwe n'ibwirizwa rya Universal Design for Learning (UDL) riva kuri CAST. ",
      "use_this_to_articulate_to_administrato": "Koresha iki kugira ngo usobanurire abayobozi canke abasuzuma inkunga ukuntu AlloFlow ishira mu ngiro UDL.",
      "feature": "Ikiranga",
