      "last_14_days": "Iminsi 14 iheze:",
      "the_1_2_trick": "Uburyo bwa 1/2",
      "let_your_number_be_n_the_sequence_n_1_": "Reka igiharuro cawe cibe n. Urukurikirane: (n+1) × 2 + 4 − 6 = 2n + 2 + 4 − 6 = 2n. Gabura na 2 → n. Kuramwo ic'intango → 0. Rindira — ivyo bitanga 0, atari 1. Gerageza: n → (n+1)×2 = 2n+2 → +4 = 2n+6 → −6 = 2n → ÷2 = n → −ic'intango = 0. \"Uburyo\" bwishimikira ku ma-constant yinyegeje mu rukurikirane.",
      "sum_of_unit_fractions": "Igiteranyo c'ibice vy'unite",
      "each_term_is_half_the_previous_the_tot": "Buri jambo ni igice kimwe kabiri c'iryabanje. Igiteranyo cegera 1 ariko ntigishika na rimwe. Uru ni urukurikirane rwa geometric rutagira iherezo rufise ijambo rya mbere 1/2 n'igiharuro 1/2: S = (1/2) / (1 − 1/2) = 1. Ni co gituma paradox y'ivyokugenda ya Zeno ishobora gutororwa mu mibare.",
      "the_harmonic_series": "Urukurikirane rwa harmonic",
      "even_though_each_term_is_small_the_ser": "Naho buri jambo ari rito, urukurikirane rurasakara. Kugira ngo urenge 100, ukeneye hafi 1.5 × 10^43 amajambo. Ivyo vyerekanywe na Nicole Oresme mu myaka ya 1300 akoresheje gukusanya: 1/3 + 1/4 > 1/4 + 1/4 = 1/2; 1/5+...+1/8 > 4 × 1/8 = 1/2; ushobora buri gihe kurondera 1/2 iyindi yo kongerako.",
      "farey_sequences": "Inkurikirane za Farey",
      "check_1_4_and_1_3_4_1_1_3_1_check_2_5_": "Raba 1/4 na 1/3: (4)(1) − (1)(3) = 1. Raba 2/5 na 1/2: (5)(1) − (2)(2) = 1. Iyi ngeso ikora igiti ca Stern-Brocot c'ibiharuro vyose vya rationnel.",
