      "3_4_means_3_divided_by_4_type_3_4_into": "3/4 bisigura «3 bigabanyijwe na 4». Andika 3 ÷ 4 kuri kalkuleteri iyo ari yo yose: 0.75. Umurongo w'igice na ÷ bisigura kimwe.",
