      "the_number_line_proves_it": "Umurongo w'imibare urabigaragaza. ",
      "the_point_at_1_4_is_the_same_point_as_": "Ahantu kuri 1/4 ni ho hamwe na 0.25. Ahantu hamwe, amazina abiri.",
      "some_terminate_some_repeat": "Bimwe birarangira, ibindi birasubiramo. ",
      "1_2_0_5_stops_1_4_0_25_stops_1_3_0_333": "1/2 = 0.5 (birahagarara). 1/4 = 0.25 (birahagarara). 1/3 = 0.333… (bisubiramo iteka). Umubare ushira hasi niwo ufata icemezo: nigabanijwemo gusa na 2 na 5, birarangira. Bitabaye ivyo birasubiramo. Raba ikimenyetso ↻ ku ikarita y'igikubo.",
