      "2_4_6_8_the_2_times_table_walking_skip": "2, 4, 6, 8… = imbonerahamwe yo kuba ya 2 igenda. Kubara ku 5 na 10 bitegura amafaranga n'igihe. Kubara usubira inyuma ku 3 bitegura gukuramwo no kugabanya. Umurongo werekana injana.",
