      "margin_of_safety_2_kcal_11": "Umupaka w'umutekano: ~2 kcal (11%)",
      "that_is_an_incredibly_thin_margin_a_st": "Uwo ni umupaka muto cane utangaje. Umuyaga ukomeye wo imbere, imbere y'ubukonje, canke kugera ku nkombe hamwe no kubura ibiro vya 10% bishobora kuba urupfu. Ni yo mpamvu ubwiza bw'ahantu ho gutura ho guhagarara ari ",
      "literally_life_or_death": "ikibazo c'ubuzima canke urupfu mu vy'ukuri",
