      "push_through_the_weather": "Sunika unyuze mu kirere",
      "find_shelter_and_wait": "Rondera ubuhungiro utegereze",
      "detour_around": "Zenguruka",
      "keep_flying": "Bandanya kuguruka",
      "land_and_rest": "Manuka uruhuke",
      "ride_thermals": "Urira imigezi y'ubushuhe",
      "animated_night_sky_showing_nocturnal_b": "Ikirere c'ijoro c'animasiyo cerekana kwimuka kw'inyoni z'ijoro. Inyenyeri zirabagirana hafi y'Inyenyeri y'Amajaruguru, imirongo y'umurima wa rukuruzi igoramye mu kirere, kandi umukumbi muto wimuka unyuze mu ishusho. Cerekana uko inyoni zikoresha inyenyeri no kumva rukuruzi mu kuyobora kw'ijoro.",
