      "what_you_can_do": "🌱 Ico Ushobora Gukora",
      "lights_out": "Zimya Amatara: ",
      "turn_off_unnecessary_lights_during_spr": "Zimya amatara adakenewe mu gihe co kwimuka kw'impeshi n'itumba (Ntwarante-Rusama, Myandagaro-Munyonyo). N'inyubako imwe yijimye ishobora gukiza amagana y'inyoni ku ijoro.",
      "window_decals": "Ibimenyetso vy'Amadirisha: ",
      "apply_bird_safe_decals_to_windows_bird": "Shira ibimenyetso birinda inyoni ku madirisha. Inyoni zibona muri ikirahure ishusho y'ikirere n'ibiti, ntabwo ari ikirahure ubwaco. Ibimenyetso bishizwe ku ntera ya sm 5 bimena amashusho.",
      "native_plants": "Ibimera vy'Igihugu: ",
      "plant_native_trees_and_shrubs_that_pro": "Tera ibiti n'ibihuru vy'igihugu bikora imbuto kandi bikurura udukoko — lisansi y'ingenzi ku nyoni zimuka. Ibimera bidasanzwe vy'igihugu akenshi ntabwo bifite udukoko inyoni zikeneye.",
      "keep_cats_inside": "Gumana Amakati Imbere: ",
      "indoor_cats_live_longer_healthier_live": "Amakati yo mu nzu abaho igihe kirekire, afite ubuzima bwiza kandi akiza inyoni. Buri wese aratsinda.",
      "citizen_science": "Ubumenyi bw'Abaturage: ",
      "use_apps_like_ebird_cornell_lab_to_rep": "Koresha porogaramu nka eBird (Cornell Lab) kugira ngo utange raporo yo kwitegereza inyoni. Amakuru yawe afasha abahanga gukurikirana igihe co kwimuka n'ibigenda vy'umubare.",
      "support_habitat": "Shigikira Aho Batura: ",
      "advocate_for_wetland_protection_and_re": "Vugira kurengera ibishanga no gushira ingufu z'umuyaga mu buryo bwuzuye inshingano mu muryango wawe.",
      "did_you_know": "🤔 Wari Uzi?",
      "on_peak_migration_nights": "Ku majoro yo hejuru yo kwimuka ",
      "over_500_million_birds": "inyoni zirenga miliyoni 500",
      "are_in_the_air_over_north_america_simu": " ziba mu kirere hejuru ya Amerika y'Amajaruguru icarimwe. Sitasiyo za radar y'ikirere zimenya ibicu binini vy'inyoni zimuka ziguruka izuba rirenga. Ushobora kuraba kwimuka mu gihe nyaco kuri BirdCast (birdcast.info).",
      "most_songbird_migration_happens_at_nig": "Kwimuka kwinshi kw'inyoni ziririmba kubera nijoro, iyo umuyaga utuje, inyamanswa ari nkeya, kandi inyenyeri zigaragara mu kuyobora. Inyoni zikoresha ",
      "setting_sun": "izuba rirenga",
      "to_calibrate_their_star_compass_at_dus": " kugira ngo zishireho busole yazo y'inyenyeri mu mugoroba.",
      "magnetic_sense": "Kumva rukuruzi",
      "of_birds_may_work_through_quantum_mech": " kw'inyoni bishobora gukora binyuze mu mekanike ya quantum. Poroteyine za cryptochrome mu maso y'inyoni zishobora gukoresha ihuriro rya quantum kugira ngo zimenye umurima wa rukuruzi w'Isi — bituma kuyobora kw'inyoni kuba kimwe mu bikorwa bike vy'ibinyabuzima bishingira kuri fiziki ya quantum.",
      "some_bird_species_can_detect_the": "Ubwoko bumwe bw'inyoni bushobora kumenya ",
      "polarization_pattern": "uburyo bwa polarizasiyo",
      "of_sunlight_even_through_heavy_cloud_c": " bw'urumuri rw'izuba ndetse no binyuze mu bicu biremereye, bikoresha ba-cône bihariye vyumva UV muri retine yabo. Ibi bisigura ndetse no ku minsi y'ibicu inyoni zishobora kumenya ahantu h'izuba kandi zikagumana inzira yazo.",
      "the_brain_s_memory_center_is_significa": " (ikigo c'ububiko bw'ubwonko) ni kinini cane mu bwoko bw'inyoni zimuka kuruta ubwoko butimuka. Mu vy'ukuri kirakura mu gihe co kwimuka, congera ba-neuron bashasha mu buryo bwitwa neurogenesis y'abakuru. Kigabanuka nanone nyuma yo kwimuka. Iyi plastiki y'ibihe y'ubwonko ni agace k'ingenzi ka siyansi y'imyakura.",
      "migration_vocabulary": "📖 Amagambo yo Kwimuka",
      "back_to_stem_lab_tool_list": "Subira ku rutonde rw'ibikoresho vya STEM Lab",
      "back": "Subira",
      "migration_wind_lab_sections": "Ibice vya Laboratwari yo Kwimuka n'Umuyaga",
      "fatal": "Vyica",
      "energy_budget_50_of_distance_bird_woul": "Ingengo y'ingufu < 50% vy'intera — inyoni yaba ipfa n'inzara hagati mu nzira. Guhagarara ni itegeko.",
      "borderline": "Ku Mupaka",
      "energy_budget_near_distance_possible_w": "Ingengo y'ingufu hafi y'intera — bishoboka hamwe n'umuyaga wuzuye wo inyuma, bitaba ivyo guhagarara ni itegeko.",
      "feasible": "Birashoboka",
      "single_leg_flight_realistic_but_tight_": "Indege y'intambwe imwe ni iy'ukuri ariko ikaze. Ubwoko bwinshi bwongera lisansi hagati mu nzira nubwo bimeze bityo.",
      "comfortable": "Vyoroshe",
      "distance_is_well_within_energy_budget_": "Intera iri neza mu ngengo y'ingufu. Kwihangana kw'urwego rwa Bar-tailed Godwit.",
      "easy": "Vyoroshe Cane",
      "3_reserve_either_short_distance_or_ove": "Ububiko bwa 3× canke birenga. Canke intera ngufi canke ububiko bw'ibinure bw'inyongera.",
      "energy_inquiry_can_the_bird_make_it": "🔬 Iperereza ku Ngufu — Inyoni Ishobora Kubigeraho?",
      "pick_wingspan_mass_headwind_formation_": "Toranya ubugari bw'ijaba, ibiro, umuyaga wo imbere, imiterere n'intera. Hanura imiterere y'ingufu. Nta amanota, nta kugaragaza.",
      "total_need": "Ibikenewe Vyose",
