      "reset": "Subiza",
      "your_hypothesis_which_parameter_forces": "Iciyumviro cawe (ni iyihe parametero itera guhagarara kwinshi kurusha?)",
      "e_g_v_formation_savings_only_pay_off_a": "urugero Kubika kw'imiterere ya V bitanga inyungu gusa hejuru ya km 1,500, kubera ko igiciro c'indege kiganje...",
      "i_m_stuck_show_open_questions": "🤔 Naciwe intege — Erekana ibibazo vyugurutse",
      "open_questions_no_answer_key": "Ibibazo vyugurutse (nta rupfunguzo rw'igisubizo)",
      "why_would_a_heavier_bird_necessarily_n": "Kuki inyoni iremereye yakenera ingufu nyinshi kuri buri km — ibi bifitanye isano ite no gukurura?",
      "a_10_m_s_headwind_doubles_the_work_wha": "Umuyaga wo imbere wa 10 m/s wongera kabiri akazi — bizagenda bite nimba igice c'urugendo gifite umuyaga wo inyuma wa 10 m/s?",
      "why_is_v_formation_savings_about_22_wh": "Kuki kubika kw'imiterere ya V ari hafi 22%? Ni ikihe giciro cayo ku nyoni iyobora?",
      "how_does_a_hummingbird_4_g_1500_km_gul": "Ni gute hummingbird (garamu 4, kwambuka Ikigobe ca Mexico km 1,500) irokoka kwimuka kwayo?",
      "i_can_explain_why_this_profile_yields_": "Nshobora gusigura impamvu iyi profayili itanga iyi miterere y'ingufu.",
      "explain_in_your_own_words": "Sigura mu magambo yawe bwite...",
      "inquiry_widget_no_score_no_reveal_no_a": "Widget y'iperereza — nta amanota, nta kugaragaza, nta mwuzure w'ibisubizo. Icitegererezo c'ingufu ni icy'urugero (gukurura ∝ m^0.67 / ubugari bw'ijaba). Kubika kw'imiterere ya V bitandukanye ~10 kugeza 30% bitewe n'ubwoko n'ahantu (Lissaman & Shollenberger 1970, umupaka wo hejuru w'inyigisho; ibipimo mu ndege birimwo Weimerskirch et al. 2001 ku bapelikani na Portugal et al. 2014 ku ba-ibis). Widget ikoresha 22% nk'igereranyo co hagati. Ku bijanye n'ubumenyi bw'ibinyabuzima nyabwo bw'ahantu ho guhagarara, raba ibitabo vy'ibanze.",
      "v_formation_flying": "Kuguruka kw'Imiterere ya V",
      "trailing_birds_catch_the_upwash_from_t": "Inyoni zo inyuma zifata umwuka-hejuru w'inyoni iri imbere — kubika ingufu 20-30%. Umwanya w'ubuyobozi urazunguruka kubera ko inyoni iri imbere ikora akazi kenshi kurusha.",
      "wind_currents_thermals": "Imigezi y'Umuyaga + Imigezi y'Ubushuhe",
      "birds_read_pressure_gradients_we_canno": "Inyoni zisoma ba-gradient b'umuvuduko tudashobora kumva. Umwuka-hejuru, umugezi w'impinga n'inkingi z'ubushuhe ni inzira inyamanswa ziguruka kilometero amagana zitwika hafi kalori zeru.",
      "migration_routes_flyways": "Inzira zo Kwimuka + Inzira zo Kuguruka",
