      "the_amazon_generates_half_its_own_rain": "Amazon itanga kimwe ca kabiri c'imvura yayo. Hamwe no gutema amashamba 20–25% + ubushuhe buzamuka, ifite ivyago vyo guhinduka iva ku ishamba ry'imvura ikaja ku isambu. Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwerekana ko urubibi rwegereye 2°C ku gipimo co gutema c'ubu.",
      "permafrost_methane_release": "Gusohora Methane kwa Permafrost",
      "arctic_permafrost_holds_twice_the_carb": "Permafrost ya Arctique ifite karubone incuro ebyiri z'iri mu kirere ubu. Ishuha 3–4× vuba kuruta impuzandengo y'isi, isanzwe irashonga ikanasohora CO₂ na methane (bikomeye 28× kuruta CO₂ mu myaka 100).",
      "west_antarctic_ice_sheet": "Urubura rw'Antarctique y'Uburengerazuba",
      "marine_based_ice_sheets_anchored_below": "Urubura rushingiye ku nyanja rwakomejwe munsi y'urwego rw'inyanja. Amazi ashushe y'inyanja arayarigata avuye hasi. Urubura rwa Thwaites (“Doomsday Glacier”) ni co cago nyamukuru. Guhirima bizazamura urwego rw'inyanja metero 3.3 (11 ft).",
      "boreal_forest_die_off": "Gupfa kw'Ishamba rya Boréal",
      "northern_coniferous_forests_russia_can": "Amashamba y'amajaruguru y'ibihuru (Uburusiya, Kanada, Scandinavia) ari mu mihangayiko iterwa n'ubushuhe, udukoko tw'ibishishwa, n'inkongi z'amashamba. Guhinduka burundu bikaba ubwatsi bishobora gusohora karubone nyinshi cane yabitswe.",
      "gulf_of_maine_rapid_warming": "Ubushuhe Bwihuse bwa Gulf of Maine",
      "the_gulf_of_maine_has_warmed_faster_th": "Gulf of Maine yashushe vuba kuruta 99% vy'inyanja z'isi kuva 1980 — hafi 0.5°F kuri buri myaka icumi, hafi 3× impuzandengo y'inyanja ku isi. Umuyaga ukonje wa Labrador wagabanutse mu gihe amazi ashushe ya Gulf Stream ageze mu majaruguru cane, ari kuvugurura urusobe rw'ibiribwa mu gihe nyaco kuva ku shingiro. Imiryango yo ku nkombe ya Penobscot, Passamaquoddy, Maliseet, na Mi’kmaq bari barandika iyi mihindagurikire mu nyandiko z'akanwa mu myaka mirongo mbere y'uko satelite zivyemeza.",
      "onshore_wind_turbines": "Turbine z'Umuyaga zo ku Butaka",
      "cheapest_electricity_worldwide_in_2024": "Amashanyarazi ahenze gake ku isi mu 2024. Ubushobozi bwikuba kabiri buri mwaka mu turere twinshi.",
      "utility_scale_solar_farms": "Imirima y'Izuba y'Urwego rwa Serivisi",
      "cheapest_electricity_in_history_grid_i": "Amashanyarazi ahenze gake mu mateka. Guhuza urusobe ni co kibazo nyamukuru ubu.",
      "rooftop_solar": "Izuba ryo ku Gisenge",
      "distributed_resilient_typical_5kw_syst": "Vyatataniye + bikomeye. Kugarura amafaranga ya sisitemu isanzwe ya 5kW: imyaka 6–10.",
      "reduced_food_waste": "Kugabanya Gutakaza Ibiryo",
      "1_3_of_food_is_wasted_preventing_waste": "1/3 vy'ibiryo birapfa ubusa. Kubuza gutakaza birinda methane iva mu irunda KANDI isohoka ryo guhinga ibiryo.",
      "plant_rich_diets": "Imirire Ikungahaye ku Bimera",
      "not_100_vegan_even_cutting_beef_3_a_we": "Ntabwo ari 100% vegan — no kugabanya inyama y'inka 3× mu cumweru bifite ingaruka nini. Birekura ubutaka bwo kongera guteramo amashamba.",
      "tropical_forest_restoration": "Kuvugurura Ishamba ry'Ubushuhe",
      "restore_125m_hectares_protects_biodive": "Vugurura hegitari 125M. Birinda ubwinshi bw'ibinyabuzima + bikurura CO₂ binyuze mu photosynthèse.",
      "temperate_forest_restoration": "Kuvugurura Ishamba ry'Ikirere Coroheje",
      "plant_where_natural_conditions_support": "Tera aho imiterere karemano ishigikira ikura. Inyungu z'inyongera: gukonjesha, kurinda ikigega c'amazi.",
      "silvopasture": "Uburagi bw'Amashamba",
      "integrating_trees_into_grazing_land_li": "Kwinjiza ibiti mu butaka bw'inzuri. Amatungo abona igicucu; ubutaka bubika karubone 4× kuruta inzuri zambaye ubusa.",
      "regenerative_agriculture": "Ubuhinzi Bwongera Kubaka",
      "no_till_cover_crops_diverse_rotations_": "Kutarima + imyaka ipfuka + kuzunguruka bitandukanye. Vyubaka karubone yo mu butaka mu gihe bibungabunga umusaruro.",
      "peatlands_protection": "Kurinda Ubutaka bwa Peat",
      "peatlands_store_3_more_carbon_than_for": "Ubutaka bwa peat bubika karubone 3× kuruta amashamba ku isi. Peat yumye = usohora munini.",
      "refrigerant_management": "Gucunga Ibikonjesha",
      "hfcs_are_1_000_9_000_more_potent_than_": "Gaze za HFCs zikomeye 1,000–9,000× kuruta CO₂. Ivugururwa rya Kigali (2016) rirazivanaho buhoro.",
      "electric_vehicles_personal": "Imodoka z'Amashanyarazi (bwite)",
      "evs_produce_50_70_less_lifetime_emissi": "EV zisohora isohoka ry'ubuzima bwose 50–70% gake kuruta lisansi — biratera imbere uko urusobe rusukuye.",
      "public_transit_rail": "Ubwikorezi rusange + Gari ya moshi",
      "electric_trains_move_a_passenger_km_at": "Gari za moshi z'amashanyarazi zitwara umugenzi-km ku 1/10 vy'isohoka ry'imodoka.",
      "bike_infrastructure": "Ibikorwa remezo vy'Amagare",
      "dutch_cycling_cities_have_1_3_the_tran": "Imiji y'amagare y'Ubuholandi ifite 1/3 vy'isohoka ry'ubwikorezi. Ibikorwa remezo bishinga imyitwarire.",
      "building_retrofits": "Kuvugurura Amazu",
      "insulation_heat_pumps_led_lighting_us_": "Isolation + pompe z'ubushuhe + amatara ya LED. Amazu ya Amerika akoresha 40% vy'ingufu z'ibanze.",
      "heat_pumps": "Pompe z'Ubushuhe",
      "3_4_more_efficient_than_gas_furnaces_w": "Zikora neza 3–4× kuruta amatanura ya gaze. Zikora kugeza −15°C mu bwoko bugezweho bw'ikirere gikonje.",
      "girls_education_family_planning": "Uburezi bw'Abakobwa no Kuboneza Uruvyaro",
      "consistently_top_ranked_educated_women": "Buri gihe ku isonga. Abagore bize bafite abana bake KANDI ubuzima bufite ingaruka nini. Vyiyongera mu bisekuru.",
      "clean_cookstoves": "Amashiga Asukuye yo Guteka",
      "replaces_wood_charcoal_fires_benefits_": "Bisimbura umuriro w'inkwi/amakara. Inyungu: ikirere + ihumana ry'umwuka wo mu nzu (rwica 4M/umwaka) + gutema amashamba.",
      "kelp_reforestation_ocean": "Kongera Gutera Kelp (inyanja)",
      "grows_60_faster_than_land_trees_seques": "Ikura 60× vuba kuruta ibiti vyo ku butaka. Ibika CO₂ + isubiza uburovyi + ifumbire.",
