      "solutions_toolkit": "Igikoresho c'Ibisubizo",
      "drawdown_ranks_100_solutions_by_gigato": "Drawdown ishira ibisubizo 100 ku rutonde ku gigatoni za CO₂ zirinzwe. Ibikonjesha, gutakaza ibiryo, no kwigisha abakobwa biri ku isonga — atari ivyo abantu benshi biyumvira.",
