      "locked_in_at_1_5_c_sustained_warming_m": "Bipfundikiye ku ~1.5°C vy'ubushuhe bukomeje. Ubwinshi bwo kwitoza ku nkombe biracashoboka hifashishijwe inkuta z'inyanja, kwisubiraho biyobowe.",
      "associated_with_2_5_c_warming_displace": "Bifitanye isano na ~2.5°C vy'ubushuhe. Vyimura abantu benshi kuruta intambara iyo ari yo yose mu mateka. Umuraba w'inkubi w'inyanja uba ikiza ku turere two mu gihugu.",
      "likely_by_2300_at_3_c_entire_nations_l": "Bishoboka mu 2300 kuri 3°C. Amahanga yose atakaza ubutaka bwo gutuura. New Orleans, Venise, n'igice kinini ca Vietnam.",
