      "you_hit_deep_decarbonization_across_se": "Wageze ku ivanwaho ry'imbitse rya karubone mu nzego zose, wubatse ubukomeye, kandi ushira uburinganire hagati. Uku ni ko impinduka y'ikirere yatsinze igaragara iyo amasezerano y'imibereho abandanya.",
      "decarbonized_but_uneven": "Vyakuweho Karubone ariko Bitangana",
      "significant_decarbonization_across_the": "Ivanwaho rikomeye rya karubone mu nzego z'ingufu n'ubwikorezi, ariko kwitoza n'ubutabera vyasigaye inyuma. Imirongo ya karubone ni myiza; ihuriro rya politiki ni ridakomeye.",
