      "cns_brain_spinal_cord_and_pns_31_spina": "CNS (ubwonko + uruti rw'umugongo) na PNS (amakipe 31 y'imyakura y'umugongo, amakipe 12 y'imyakura y'igihanga, sisitemu y'imyakura yigenga).",
      "brain": "Ubwonko",
      "lightest_sleep_transition_from_wakeful": "Ibitotsi vyoroshe cane — guhinduka uva mu kuba maso. Kunyeganyega gahoro kw'amaso, imbaraga z'imitsi zigabanuka. Guhinda kwa hypnic (kunyeganyega kwa myoclonic) birasanzwe. Vyoroshe gukanguka. Imiraba ya vertex ikarishe igaragara kuri EEG.",
      "true_sleep_begins_core_body_temperatur": "Ibitotsi nyavyo bitangira. Ubushuhe bwo hagati bw'umubiri buragabanuka, imikubitire y'umutima igabanuka. Sleep spindles (guturika kwa thalamocortical) birinda ibitotsi kandi bikahamya kwibuka kwo kwimuka. K-complexes ni imiraba minini yitabira ibimenyetso vyo hanze.",
      "deep_slow_wave_sleep_sws_most_restorat": "Ibitotsi vyimbitse/vy'umuraba gahoro (SWS). Iciciro gisubiza imbaraga cane. Gusohora hormone y'imikurire bigera hejuru. Sisitemu ya glymphatic isukura imyanda y'ubwonko (amyloid-β). Guhamya kwibuka gutangaza biba. Bigoye cane gukanguka; ubunebwe bw'ibitotsi iyo ukanguwe.",
      "dreaming_stage_brain_is_highly_active_": "Iciciro c'inzozi. Ubwonko burakora cane (nk'ukuba maso) ariko umubiri urakumira (atonia binyuze mu kubuza kw'igihuru c'ubwonko imyakura yo kwimuka). Kunyeganyega vuba kw'amaso guhuza. Gutunganya kwibuka kw'amarangamutima no gukemura ibibazo mu buhanga. Ibihe birekurura mu ijoro.",
      "cerebral_cortex_4_lobes": "Igikonoshwa c'Ubwonko (Ibice 4)",
      "brodmann_areas_map_52_cytoarchitectura": "Uturere twa Brodmann tugaragaza uturere 52 tw'imiterere y'ingirabuzimafatizo. Igikonoshwa c'ibanze co kwimuka (agace 4), igikonoshwa c'ibanze c'ivyiyumviro vy'umubiri (utuce 3,1,2), igikonoshwa c'ibanze co kubona (agace 17), igikonoshwa c'ibanze co kumva (utuce 41,42). Igikonoshwa ca prefrontal ni co ca nyuma kubona myelin (~imyaka 25).",
      "cerebellum": "Akabwonko",
      "purkinje_cells_are_among_the_largest_n": "Ingirabuzimafatizo za Purkinje ziri mu myakura minini cane, buri imwe yakira nka 200,000 z'inyunge za synaptic. Igikonoshwa ca cerebellar gifite ivyiciro 3: molecular, Purkinje, granular. Ubushakashatsi bushasha bwerekana uruhare rwavyo mu kumva, amarangamutima, n'ururimi.",
      "brainstem_midbrain_pons_medulla": "Igihuru c'Ubwonko (Ubwonko bwo Hagati, Pons, Medulla)",
      "contains_nuclei_for_cranial_nerves_iii": "Kirimwo nuclei z'imyakura y'igihanga III–XII. Sisitemu ya reticular activating (RAS) ni \"buto yo gucana\" y'ubwonko — kwangirika bitera koma. Kwambuka kwa piramide muri medulla: kwambuka kwo kwimuka bisigura kugenzura kwo kwimuka kw'uruhande runyuranye.",
      "hippocampus": "Hippocampus",
      "memory_replay_during_sleep_hippocampal": "Gusubiramwo kwibuka mu gihe c'ibitotsi: imyakura ya hippocampal \"isubiramwo\" ivyabaye ku manywa mu bitotsi vya N3, yimura kwibuka kuri neocortex. Ingirabuzimafatizo za grid mu gikonoshwa ca entorhinal zitanga ibipimo vy'umwanya ku ngirabuzimafatizo z'ahantu za hippocampal.",
      "amygdala": "Amygdala",
      "fear_conditioning_pathway_auditory_cor": "Inzira yo kwigisha ubwoba: igikonoshwa co kumva → amygdala y'uruhande → amygdala yo hagati → hypothalamus (igisubizo c'umuhangayiko) + PAG (guhagarara). Imikoranire ya amygdala-prefrontal itanga uburyo bwo kugenzura amarangamutima — urufatiro rw'ubuvuzi bwa CBT.",
      "thalamus": "Thalamus",
      "key_nuclei_vpl_vpm_somatosensory_relay": "Nuclei z'ingenzi: VPL/VPM (koherereza ivyiyumviro vy'umubiri), LGN (koherereza kubona kuri V1), MGN (koherereza kumva kuri A1), pulvinar (kwitondera), itsinda rya nuclei ryo imbere (kwibuka, uruziga rwa Papez).",
      "hypothalamus": "Hypothalamus",
      "thermostat_analogy_anterior_hypothalam": "Ingero ya thermostat: hypothalamus yo imbere itera gukonja (kwaguka kw'imitsi, kubira ivyuya); hypothalamus yo inyuma itera gushuha (guhinda umushitsi, guhina imitsi). Umuriro = urwego rwazamuwe na prostaglandins ziturutse ku ndwara.",
      "corpus_callosum": "Corpus Callosum",
      "split_brain_experiments_revealed_hemis": "Ubushakashatsi bwo kugabanya ubwonko bwagaragaje ubuhanga bw'ibice: uruhande rw'ibumoso = ururimi, ubwenge; uruhande rw'iburyo = gutunganya umwanya, vyuzuye. Amakuru atangwa ku murima umwe wo kubona atunganywa n'uruhande runyuranye.",
      "basal_ganglia": "Basal Ganglia",
