      "muscles_attach_to_bones_via_tendons_an": "Imitsi ifatana n'amagufa binyuze mu misumari kandi ikurura ku ngingo, ikora sisitemu za levier. Urwungano rw'amagufa rutanga levier zikomeye; imitsi itanga imbaraga zo gukurura.",
