      "patella_patellofemoral_joint": "Igufwa ry'ivi / ingingo ya patellofemoral",
      "patellofemoral_pain_syndrome_occurs_wh": "Indwara y'ububabare bwa patellofemoral iba iyo igufwa ry'ivi ridatembera neza mu muferege waryo ku gufwa ry'itako. Igitutu gisubiramo kiva mu kwiruka gitera kubabara kwa cartilage. Ubuvuzi burimo kubandanya quad, guhamya urukiro, no guhindura ibikorwa.",
