      "supraspinatus_tendon_rotator_cuff": "Umusumari wa supraspinatus (rotator cuff)",
      "the_supraspinatus_is_the_most_commonly": "Supraspinatus ni umutsi wa rotator cuff utabuka cane. Unyura munsi ya acromion aho uhura n'igitutu no gutabuka. Akazi ko hejuru y'umutwe nko gusiga irangi kongera iki kaga cane.",
      "racing_heart_after_exercise": "Umutima Ukubita Vuba Nyuma yo Kwimenyereza Umubiri",
      "which_structure_controls_the_normal_he": "Ni iyihe miterere igenzura imikubitire isanzwe y'umutima?",
      "sinoatrial_sa_node": "Sinoatrial (SA) node",
      "the_sa_node_in_the_right_atrium_is_the": "SA node iri mu atrium y'iburyo ni pacemaker karemano y'umutima. Mu gihe co kwimenyereza umubiri gukomeye, adrenaline ishobora gutera imikubitire itagira ingaruka mbi mu gihe imikubitire y'umutima ihindagurika. Arrhythmias zibandanya zigomba gusuzumwa kugira ngo hakurweho indwara y'umutima y'imiterere.",
      "the_numb_hand": "Ukuboko Kwapfuye",
      "which_nerve_is_being_compressed": "Ni uwuhe mwakura ukandamizwa?",
      "median_nerve_carpal_tunnel_syndrome": "Umwakura wa median (indwara ya carpal tunnel)",
      "carpal_tunnel_syndrome_is_compression_": "Indwara ya carpal tunnel ni ukwandamizwa kw'umwakura wa median munsi ya flexor retinaculum ku ijoro ry'ukuboko. Umwakura wa median utanga ivyiyumviro ku rutoki runini n'intoki 3.5 za mbere. Gukoresha ijoro ry'ukuboko kenshi ni impamvu ikomeye y'akaga.",
      "the_swollen_neck_node": "Akabunda k'Ijosi Kavyimvye",
      "what_diagnosis_must_be_urgently_ruled_": "Ni iyihe ndwara igomba gukurwaho vyihutirwa?",
      "lymphoma_hodgkin_lymphoma": "Lymphoma (Hodgkin lymphoma)",
      "painless_lymphadenopathy_with_b_sympto": "Kuvyimba kw'utubunda twa lymph bidababaza, hamwe n'ibimenyetso vya B (ivyuya vy'ijoro, gutakaza ibiro, umuriro) ni ikimenyetso gisanzwe ca Hodgkin lymphoma ku basore. Biopsy yerekana ingirabuzimafatizo za Reed-Sternberg yemeza isuzuma.",
      "the_diabetic_emergency": "Ihutirwa rya Diyabete",
      "which_cells_failed_and_what_is_the_eme": "Ni izihe ngirabuzimafatizo zananiwe, kandi ni iyihe mimerere y'ihutirwa?",
      "beta_cells_of_islets_of_langerhans_dia": "Ingirabuzimafatizo beta za islets of Langerhans; Diabetic Ketoacidosis (DKA)",
      "without_insulin_from_beta_cells_glucos": "Nta insuline iva mu ngirabuzimafatizo beta, glucose ntishobora kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo. Umubiri utwika ibinure, ukora ketones zituma amaraso aba acide. Guhumeka kwa Kussmaul kwishura mu gusohora CO2. Ubuvuzi: amazi ya IV, insuline drip, no gusimbura electrolyte.",
      "the_broken_collarbone": "Igufwa ry'Urutugu Ryavunitse",
      "why_is_the_middle_third_of_the_clavicl": "Kuki igice ca gatatu co hagati ca clavicle ari aho havunika cane?",
      "the_middle_third_is_thinnest_and_has_n": "Igice ca gatatu co hagati ni co gito kandi nta kubandanya kw'imitsi",
      "the_clavicle_is_the_most_frequently_fr": "Clavicle ni igufwa rivunika kenshi. Igice caryo ca gatatu co hagati ni co gito kandi nta kurinda kw'imitsi. Imbaraga ziva mu kugwa ku kuboko kwagurutswe zikusanyirizwa kuri iki gice gifite intege nke. Vyinshi bikira binyuze mu guhambira ukuboko.",
      "breathless_at_high_altitude": "Kubura Umwuka ku Butumburuke Buhanitse",
      "why_does_altitude_cause_these_symptoms": "Kuki ubutumburuke butera ibi bimenyetso, kandi ni iyihe miterere ihura n'igitutu cane?",
      "the_alveoli_and_respiratory_muscles_re": "Alveoli n'imitsi yo guhumeka; ogisijeni y'ikirere yagabanutse itera hypoxia",
      "at_high_altitude_atmospheric_pressure_": "Ku butumburuke buhanitse, igitutu c'ikirere kiragabanuka, kigabanya igitutu c'igice ca ogisijeni. Ogisijeni nke inyura mu ruhu rwa alveoli. Umubiri wishura mu guhumeka vuba no cane, wongera akazi k'imitsi yo guhumeka.",
