      "click_any_organ_to_see_its_structure_f": "Fyonda ku ngingo iyo ari yo yose kugira ngo urabe imiterere yayo, imikorere yayo, n'aho ihuriye. Shira hejuru kugira ngo ubone ibirango vyoroshe; fyonda kugira ngo ubone ibisobanuro birambuye.",
      "step_through_each_major_part_in_pedago": "Nyura mu buri gice kinini mu buryo bwo kwigisha. Inzira nziza cane ku bigira bwa mbere — ihuza imiterere → imikorere → guhuza mu kurebamo rimwe.",
      "cross_system_connections": "Amahuriro Hagati ya Sisitemu",
      "no_system_works_alone_the_kidney_filte": "Nta sisitemu ikora yonyine. Impyiko iyungurura amaraso (umutima n'imitsi), isubiza ADH (endocrine), isohora urée (igicuruzwa co kugogora). Shaka amahuriro.",
