      "build_the_double_helix_from_4_letters": "Ubaka double helix uhereye ku nyuguti 4",
      "a_pairs_with_t_2_bonds_g_with_c_3_wats": "A ihuza na T (bond 2), G na C (3). Watson + Crick + Franklin (1953) bakemuye iyi miterere bakoresheje X-ray crystallography. Iyo miterere yerekana uko DNA yikoporora kandi isomwa.",
      "replicate_unzip_copy_rezip": "Gukoporora — ugurura, koporora, ongera wugare",
      "helicase_splits_the_strands_dna_polyme": "Helicase itandukanya strand; DNA polymerase yubaka strand yuzuye. Semi-conservative — buri helix nshasha ifite strand ishaje imwe + nshasha imwe. Meselson na Stahl bavyerekanye mu 1958.",
      "transcribe_dna_mrna_in_the_nucleus": "Kwandika — DNA → mRNA (mu nucleus)",
      "rna_polymerase_reads_one_dna_strand_3_": "RNA polymerase isoma DNA strand imwe 3′→5′ ikubaka RNA 5′→3′. Inyuguti ni zimwe, gusa T iba U. mRNA itwara amabwiriza kugeza ku ribosome — intambwe ya mbere ya central dogma.",
      "translate_mrna_protein_at_the_ribosome": "Guhindura — mRNA → protein (ku ribosome)",
      "64_codons_20_amino_acids_the_genetic_c": "codon 64 → amino acid 20 (genetic code irenze). AUG itangura; UAA/UAG/UGA zihagarika. tRNA isoma codon, izana amino acid nyayo, yubaka peptide bond.",
      "mutate_substitution_insertion_deletion": "Guhinduka — gusimbura, kwinjiza, gukuraho",
      "point_mutation_one_letter_swapped_inse": "Point mutation — inyuguti imwe yasimbuwe. Insertion/deletion — reading frame irimuka, protein yose yo hasi yangirika. Sickle cell anemia ni A→T imwe gusa — inyuguti imwe, ingaruka ku buzima bwose.",
      "crispr_the_precision_edit": "CRISPR — guhindura mu buryo bwuzuye",
      "bacterial_immune_system_repurposed_cas": "Sisitemu y'ubudahangarwa bwa bagiteri yakoreshejwe ku kindi. Cas9 enzyme + guide RNA = umukasi wa molekile. Doudna + Charpentier batsindiye Nobel 2020. CRISPR therapy ya mbere (sickle cell) FDA yayemeje muri Kigarama 2023.",
      "protein_fold_function_malfunction": "Protein — guhina, umurimo, ikibazo",
      "sequence_determines_structure_determin": "Sequence igena structure igena umurimo. Hemoglobin itwara O₂, antibody irabimenya, enzyme ikora catalyze. AlphaFold (2020) yahanuye structure miliyoni 200 — ikibazo c'imyaka 50 cakemutse mu mezi 18.",
      "forensics_str_profiling_dna_evidence": "Siyansi y'ubutabera — STR profiling + ibimenyetso vya DNA",
      "codis_uses_20_short_tandem_repeat_str_": "CODIS ikoresha short tandem repeat (STR) loci 20. Amahirwe y'uko bihuza ari ay'igitangaza (rimwe kuri quadrillion) igihe loci zose zihuza. Innocence Project — ibihano birenga 245 vy'amakosa vyavanyweho nyuma yo gupima DNA.",
      "challenge_graded_problems": "Ikigeragezo — ibibazo bihabwa amanota",
      "practice_transcription_translation_mut": "Toza transcription, translation, gutandukanya mutation. AP Bio Big Idea 3.A.1 — DNA (rimwe na rimwe RNA) ni ishingiro ryo gutanga amakuru y'irondakoko. NGSS HS-LS3-1.",
      "battle_head_to_head_retrieval": "Urugamba — kubona amaso ku maso",
      "retrieval_practice_gamified_speed_buil": "Kwitoza kubona — mu buryo bw'umukino. Umuvuduko wubaka automaticity — igihe kuraba codon table bihinduka gukorwa vyonyine, working memory yawe iba yisanzuye ku vyiyumviro vyo hejuru, nk'uguhanura ingaruka za mutation.",
      "learn_the_central_dogma_history": "Iga — central dogma + akahise",
      "dna_rna_protein_with_retroviruses_hiv_": "DNA → RNA → protein — hamwe na retrovirus (HIV) isubira inyuma na reverse transcriptase. Crick yahimvye ijambo \"dogma\" mu 1957; nyuma avuga risigura iciyumviro, atari ukuri budahangarwa.",
      "build_a_dna_strand": "Ubaka DNA strand",
