      "helicase_unwinds_the_helix_dna_polymer": "Helicase yugurura helix; DNA polymerase isoma buri template strand ikubaka uzuzuza. Semi-conservative — buri daughter strand ifite ishaje imwe + nshasha imwe.",
      "transcription_dna_mrna": "Transcription — DNA → mRNA",
      "rna_polymerase_reads_the_template_stra": "RNA polymerase isoma template strand. Amategeko amwe ya complementarity, ariko T → U. Igisubizo — mRNA copy imwe ya single-strand, yiteguye gusohoka mu nucleus.",
