      "mutations": "Mutation",
      "point_mutations_silent_no_protein_chan": "Point mutation — silent (protein ntihinduka), missense (amino acid itandukanye), nonsense (guhagarara hakiri kare). Frameshift (insertion/deletion) akenshi irangiza vyose.",
