      "real_time_pitch_trace_volume_meter_fil": "Gukurikirana ubuhagarike bw'ijwi mu gihe nyaco + igipimo c'ijwi + ikibara amagambo yuzuza. Abavugizi batojwe bahindura ubuhagarike bw'ijwi ~30% mu nteruro; iyerekana rirambuye ritakaza ubwitondere bw'umuteze amatwi mu ~masegonda 20.",
      "practice_work_through_a_delivery": "Imyitozo — kora iyerekana ryuzuye",
      "pacing_target_150_wpm_pauses_between_i": "Intego y'umuvuduko ~amagambo 150/umunota. Guhagarara hagati y'ivyiyumviro (amasegonda 1-2) bifite uburemere bungana n'amagambo. Banza usome ivyo wanditse mu ijwi riranguruye; interuro zidasobanutse zigaragara ako kanya.",
