      "speech_rate_varies_dramatically_by_lan": "Umuvuduko w'imvugo utandukanye cane bitewe n'ururimi: Icesipanyoli + Ikiyapani ~ivyunguti 7/isegonda; Icongereza ~6; Ikimandarini ~5. Umuvuduko w'amakuru urahamye hafi ya — indimi ziremereye zivugwa buhoro.",
      "report_your_delivery_analytics": "Raporo — isesengura ry'iyerekana ryawe",
      "pace_pitch_range_filler_word_density_p": "Umuvuduko, urwego rw'ubuhagarike bw'ijwi, ubwinshi bw'amagambo yuzuza, igihe co guhagarara — buri kimwe gihabwa amanota ugereranyije n'intego zishigikiwe n'ubushakashatsi. Fyonda ku gipimo ico ari co cose kugira ngo ubone isoko + impanuro y'ubwigishe.",
      "prosody_discover_how_delivery_shapes_m": "Injana — menya uko iyerekana rikora ibisobanuro",
      "adjust_pitch_offset_pace_and_volume_ga": "Hindura ihindagurika ry'ubuhagarike bw'ijwi, umuvuduko, no kongera ijwi, hanyuma wandike ivyo ubona. Nta manota, nta vyahishuwe — kora iciyumviro cawe ku mpamvu imvugo nyinshi za TED ziri hafi y'amagambo 150/umunota.",
      "slow_deliberate": "🐢 Buhoro / witonze",
      "suited_to_emphasis_reflection_gravitas": "Bikwiye gushimangira, kwiyumvisha, uburemere.",
