      "flat_plane_parallel_postulate_holds_an": "Urwego rusanzuye. Iciyumviro-shingiro c'imirongo iteganye kirakora. Inguni z'umutatu ziteranya neza kuri 180°.",
      "surface_of_sphere_triangle_angles_sum_": "Ubuso bw'umupira. Inguni z'umutatu ziteranya KURENZA 180°. Ikirenga gihuye n'ubuso. Bikoreshwa mu buyobozi bw'amato.",
      "saddle_shaped_surface_triangle_angles_": "Ubuso bufite imiterere y'intebe-farashi. Inguni z'umutatu ziteranya MUNSI ya 180°. Imirongo iteganye myinshi inyura ku kadomo katari ku murongo.",
      "shortest_paths_on_a_surface_straight_l": "Inzira ngufi ku buso. Imirongo igororotse (Euclide); inziga nini (umupira); imirongo ya hiperubolike.",
      "largest_circles_on_a_sphere_equator_me": "Inziga nini kurusha izindi ku mupira. Ekwateri + meridiyani. Indege zikurikira inzira z'uruziga runini.",
      "euclidean_0_spherical_positive_hyperbo": "Euclide = 0. Umupira = positifu. Hiperubolike = negatifu. Ukugoramye kugena geometiri.",
      "on_sphere_of_radius_r_triangle_area_r_": "Ku mupira w'umurambararo R, ubuso bw'umutatu = R² × (igiteranyo c'inguni − π).",
