      "in_art_overstated": "Mu bugeni (vyavuzwe birenze)",
      "often_claimed_in_parthenon_mona_lisa_e": "Kenshi bivugwa muri Parthénon, Mona Lisa, n'ibindi — ibivugwa vyinshi ntibishigikiwe. Ubugeni nyabwo bw'igipimo ca zahabu: gukoresha kubishaka mu kinyejana ca 20 (Le Corbusier, Dali).",
