      "long_believed_humans_find_golden_ratio": "Igihe kirekire bemeraga ko abantu babona igipimo ca zahabu ari co ciza kurusha ibindi. Ibimenyetso bikomeye ni bike kuruta uko inkuru zizwi zivuga.",
