      "flat_sheet_can_fold_into_virtually_any": "Urupapuro rusanzuye rushobora gukunjwa muri hafi imiterere iyo ari yo yose ya 3D hamwe n'amakunja ahagije. Origami igezweho iragoye cane.",
      "real_world_space_telescopes": "Isi nyayo: telesikopi z'ikirere",
