      "distant_objects_appear_bluer_less_dist": "Ibintu vya kure bigaragara vyubuye kandi bidasobanutse bitewe no gukwira kw'ikirere.",
      "some_traditions_use_specific_angles_ra": "Imigenzo imwe ikoresha inguni + ibipimo vyihariye (amashusho ya geometiri y'Abayisilamu, mandala z'Abahindi, katedrali z'ikigotike).",
      "mathematical_artist_impossible_objects": "Umuhanzi w'imibare. Ibintu bidashoboka (imitatu ya Penrose), iyubakwa-nkweto, geometiri ya hiperubolike.",
