      "math_inquiry": "Ubushakashatsi bw'Imibare",
      "base_10_blocks_ones_tens_hundreds_thou": "Base-10 Blocks — imwe, icumi, ijana, igihumbi",
      "the_whole_point_of_place_value_made_ta": "Intego yose ya place value yakozwe ikintu USHOBORA GUKORAKORA. Imwe 10 = icumi 1; icumi 10 = ijana 1; ijana 10 = igihumbi 1. Regrouping (carrying / borrowing) igaragara neza igihe ugomba guhindura blocks n'intoki zawe.",
      "abacus_4_500_years_of_mental_arithmeti": "Abacus — imyaka 4,500 y'imibare yo mu mutwe",
      "soroban_japanese_and_suanpan_chinese_a": "Soroban (y'Ubuyapani) na Suanpan (y'Ubushinwa) biracigishwa — abahanga banesha calculators ku muvuduko mu bibazo vyinshi. Rod imwe n'imwe ni place value; imiterere ya beads NI umubare. Kuva ku kintu gikorwakora kugeza mu mutwe mu mezi make.",
      "slide_rule_logarithms_in_your_hand": "Slide Rule — logarithms mu kuboko kwawe",
      "how_engineers_multiplied_before_electr": "Uko ba injeniyeri bakubaga mbere ya calculators z'amashanyarazi: huza logarithmic scales, soma igisubizo. Apollo 11 (1969) yakoze imibare ya orbit na slide rules. Vyasimbuwe vyose gusa nyuma y'uko HP-35 isohoka mu 1972.",
      "quiz_graded_place_value_arithmetic": "Quiz — place value na arithmetic bifite amanota",
      "ccss_1_nbt_2_nbt_3_nbt_4_nbt_progressi": "Urutonde rwa CCSS 1.NBT, 2.NBT, 3.NBT, 4.NBT. Uburyo bwa concrete-pictorial-abstract (CPA, Bruner 1966) ni umugongo wa buri curriculum y'imibare yakozwe neza yo mu mashure abanza.",
      "ten_frames_the_k_2_number_sense_workho": "Ten Frames — inkingi ya number sense ya K-2",
      "a_5_by_2_grid_fill_cells_to_show_a_num": "Grid ya 5 na 2. Uzuza cells kugira ngo werekane umubare. Subitizing (kumenya ako kanya utabaze) bikura hano. CCSS K.OA.A.4: ikibazo \"ni iki gikora 10?\" ni irembo rya fluency yose ya arithmetic izaza.",
      "two_color_counters_integers_concrete": "Two-Color Counters — integers nk'ikintu gikorwakora",
      "yellow_1_red_1_a_yellow_red_pair_0_a_z": "Umuhondo = +1; umutuku = -1. Ipaji umuhondo + umutuku = 0 (\"zero pair\"). Model itomoye cane yo gutahura negative numbers na integer arithmetic. CCSS 6.NS.C.5, 7.NS.A.1.",
      "place_value_disks_bridge_to_algorithm": "Place-Value Disks — ikiraro kigana algorithm",
      "each_disk_labeled_with_its_value_1_10_": "Buri disk yanditseho agaciro kayo (1, 10, 100, 1000). Imura disks 10 z'ubwoko bumwe kugira ngo uzisimbuze 1 y'agaciro gakurikira. Ikiraro c'ivyiyumviro kuva blocks nyazo kugeza standard algorithm. CCSS 4.NBT.B.4.",
      "hundreds_chart_count_pattern_and_skip": "Hundreds Chart — bara, pattern, no gusimbuka",
      "a_10x10_grid_of_1_100_click_to_highlig": "Grid ya 10x10 ya 1-100. Fyonda kugira ngo umurikire cells. Skip-count overlays zerekana patterns za multiplication. CCSS 2.NBT.A.2: skip-counting ku 5, 10, 100.",
      "pattern_blocks_fractions_symmetry": "Pattern Blocks — fractions na symmetry",
      "hexagon_trapezoid_rhombus_triangle_squ": "Hexagon, trapezoid, rhombus, triangle, square, rhombus yagoramye. Trapezoids 6 = hexagon 1 (bityo trapezoid 1 = 1/2 ya hexagon). Rhombi 3 = hexagon 1 (bityo rhombus 1 = 1/3). Triangles 6 = hexagon 1 (bityo triangle 1 = 1/6).",
      "geoboard_polygons_on_a_peg_grid": "Geoboard — polygons ku grid ya pegs",
      "connect_pegs_with_rubber_bands_to_make": "Huza pegs na \"rubber bands\" kugira ngo ukore polygons. Pima perimeter na area. Igikoresho gakondo gikorwakora ca plane geometry na Pick's theorem.",
      "cuisenaire_rods_numbers_in_color": "Cuisenaire Rods — imibare mu ibara",
      "belgian_teacher_georges_cuisenaire_195": "Umwigisha w'Ububiligi Georges Cuisenaire (1952): rods 10, uburebure 1-10, buri imwe ifite ibara ritandukanye. Ongeraho rods kugira ngo ukore imibare mishasha. Umweru=1, umutuku=2, icatsi kigufi=3, umuhengeri=4, umuhondo=5, icatsi cijimye=6, umukara=7, umukara-ubwoya=8, ubururu=9, oranje=10.",
      "number_bonds_part_part_whole": "Number Bonds — part-part-whole",
      "the_whole_splits_into_two_parts_singap": "Igiteranyo cose kigabanyijemo ibice bibiri. Singapore Math yabikoze ikintu c'ingenzi. CCSS K.OA.A.3: gabanya 10 mu mapaji. Ibi vyubaka inzira igana kongera no gukuramwo vyose.",
      "fraction_bars_compare_and_add_fraction": "Fraction Bars — gereranya no kongeramwo fractions",
      "equal_length_bars_partitioned_into_hal": "Bars z'uburebure bungana zagabanyijwemo kabiri, gatatu, kane, gatandatu, umunani, na cumi na kabiri. Zunganya kugira ngo ugereranye. Rondera zinganya n'amaso. Igikoresho kimwe gisukuye cane ca fraction equivalence (3.NF, 4.NF).",
      "algebra_tiles_model_expressions_and_eq": "Algebra Tiles — kora model ya expressions na equations",
      "a_tile_for_1_unit_x_variable_x_square_": "Tile ya 1 (unit), x (variable), x² (square). Amabara abiri: positive na negative. Kora model ya expressions nka 2x + 3 canke factor quadratics uhuza tiles mu rectangles. CCSS 7.EE, 8.EE.",
      "cra_progression_concrete_picture_equat": "CRA Progression — concrete → ishusho → equation",
      "bruner_1966_students_master_each_conce": "Bruner (1966): abanyeshure bamenya buri concept banyuze mu nzira eshatu za representation. Tugutwara mu KIBAZO KIMWE mu nzira eshatu zose kugira ngo abstract symbol igire ishingiro mu kintu ushobora KUBONA no GUKORAKORA.",
      "challenge_hub_quick_practice_across_ev": "Ikigo c'Ibibazo — imyitozo yihuse kuri buri manipulative",
      "random_problems_spanning_all_12_manipu": "Ibibazo random bireba manipulatives 12 zose. Vyakozwe kuri distributed practice (Cepeda et al. 2006): set ngufi y'iminota itanu, ivanga ubwoko, inesha iminota makumyabiri y'ubwoko bumwe ikurikirana.",
      "glossary_math_vocabulary_with_examples": "Inkoranyamagambo — amagambo y'imibare, hamwe n'ingero",
      "vocabulary_is_the_curriculum_a_student": "Amagambo NI curriculum. Umunyeshure wumva \"regroup,\" \"compose,\" \"decompose,\" \"fluently,\" na \"place value\" incuro nyinshi mu mvugo azashira system muri we. Ibisobanuro bifatanijwe na manipulative yerekana buri kimwe.",
      "brain_teasers_classic_math_puzzles": "Ibisakuzo vy'Ubwenge — puzzles gakondo z'imibare",
      "classic_problems_that_are_solvable_sat": "Ibibazo gakondo bishobora gukemuka, binyura, kandi akenshi vyoroshe iyo manipulative iri mu kuboko. Bifite akamaro nka warm-up, ibikorwa vyo kuzuza igihe, canke imirimo y'ishingiro y'ikiganiro c'ishure.",
      "history_math_tools_through_time": "Amateka — ibikoresho vy'imibare mu bihe",
      "counting_bones_lebombo_35_000_bce_sume": "Amagufa yo kubara (Lebombo, ~35,000 BCE) → tokens za Sumeri → abacus y'Abaroma → Cuisenaire rods (1952) → uyu munsi. Buri manipulative muri iki gikoresho ni igice c'umuryango muremure w'ibikoresho vyo kwigisha.",
      "curriculum_map_which_tool_which_grade": "Ikarita ya Curriculum — igikoresho ikihe, grade iyihe",
      "a_k_5_progression_chart_showing_which_": "Chart y'urutonde rwa K-5 yerekana manipulatives zizanwa muri grade iyihe na standards zishigikira. Fyonda cell iyo ari yo yose kugira ngo wugurure ico gikoresho.",
