      "ready_to_print_activity_cards_for_smal": "Amakarita y'ibikorwa yiteguye gucapwa ku itsinda rito canke ishure ryose. Buri karita yita ku ntego, ibikoresho, intambwe, n'ikibazo co kwagura. Vyakozwe gukoreshwa NTA ka app iyi — ariko ushobora no kubinyura muri app.",
      "help_faq_2": "Ubufasha & FAQ",
      "quick_reference_answers_to_common_stud": "Ibisubizo vyihuse ku bibazo abanyeshure n'abigisha bakunze kubaza, hamwe na keyboard shortcuts, amakuru ya accessibility, n'uko wahamagara ubufasha bwa AlloFlow.",
