      "previous_2": "← Ibanza",
      "print": "🖨 Cap",
      "next_11": "Ikurikira →",
      "all_cards": "Amakarita yose:",
      "cards_are_designed_to_be_printed_and_u": "💡 Amakarita yakozwe kugira ngo acapwe akoreshwe kure ya ecran. Manipulatives nyazo z'umubiri zikirenza iza virtual kuri K-2 — kinesthetic loop ifite akamaro. ",
      "the_app_gives_you_every_manipulative_o": "App iguha MANIPULATIVE YOSE mu kuboko, ndetse n'igihe kit nyayo itari mu cumba.",
      "faq": "❓ FAQ",
      "shortcuts": "⌨ Shortcuts",
      "pitfalls": "⚠ Imitego",
      "about": "ℹ Ku bijanye",
      "keyboard_shortcuts": "Keyboard shortcuts:",
      "treating_manipulatives_as_filler_not_i": "Gufata manipulatives nk'\"ivyuzuza igihe\" si uburezi",
      "common_mistake_handing_out_blocks_and_": "Ikosa risanzwe: gutanga blocks hanyuma ugakomeza. Nta burezi busobanutse buHUZA manipulative na symbol, akenshi abanyeshure bakina n'igikinisho ntibiga ikintu gishasha. Buri gihe soza buri session ya manipulative na: \"Nyereka ku rupapuro ico ukoze.\"",
      "keeping_students_on_the_concrete_stage": "Kubika abanyeshure ku ntambwe ya concrete igihe kirekire",
      "a_4th_grader_who_still_needs_blocks_fo": "Umunyeshure wa grade 4 ukiKENEYE blocks ku 23 + 47 afite ikibazo. Blocks zari scaffold; nizidakurwaho na rimwe, fluency ntizakura. Ja kuri representational (amashusho) muri grade 2-3, kuri abstract (symbols) muri grade 3-4. Subira kuri concrete gusa ku concepts nshasha.",
      "skipping_the_representational_stage": "Gusimbuka intambwe ya representational",
      "most_rushed_teachers_go_from_blocks_st": "Abigisha benshi bihuta bava kuri blocks baja ku buryo butaziguye kuri \"none andika 4 + 5 = 9.\" Ivyo bisimbuka intambwe ya iconic (gushushanya dots, number lines, arrays). Witzel, Mercer & Miller (2003) basanze icuho ari aho abanyeshure benshi baguye. Buri gihe ongeramo intambwe y'ishusho.",
      "letting_students_always_work_alone": "Kureka abanyeshure gukora bonyine buri gihe",
      "manipulative_work_without_talk_is_half": "Umurimo wa manipulative NTA KUVUGA ni kimwe ca kabiri c'agaciro kawo. Fatanya abanyeshure babiri; saba babavuge ico bakora. Kuvuga NI intambwe yo kubandanya yimura igikorwa kuva \"intoki zizi\" kugeza \"umutwe uzi.\"",
      "confusing_speed_with_understanding": "Kuvanga umuvuduko no gutahura",
      "timed_fact_fluency_drills_can_make_stu": "Drills za fact-fluency zifite igihe zishobora gutuma abanyeshure baba bihuse muri procedures batasobanukiwe (raba ubushakashatsi bwa \"math anxiety\": Boaler 2014). Umurimo wa manipulative buhoro NTU ni munsi y'umurimo w'urupapuro wihuse kuri K-3.",
      "mismatching_manipulative_to_standard": "Kudahuza manipulative na standard",
      "don_t_use_the_abacus_to_teach_fraction": "Ntukoreshe abacus kwigisha fractions. Ntukoreshe pattern blocks kwigisha place value. Ikarita ya Curriculum yerekana manipulative ikora kuri CCSS iyihe — tangura aho.",
      "praising_effort_but_not_strategy": "Gushimira imbaraga ariko atari strategy",
      "saying_great_job_rewards_completion_sa": "Kuvuga \"akazi keza!\" bihemba kurangiza. Kuvuga \"Nabonye ugerageje trapezoids 3 mbere yo guhindura triangles 6 — ni iki catumye uhindura?\" bihemba kwiyumvira. Ba usobanutse.",
      "ignoring_student_invented_strategies": "Kwirengagiza strategies abanyeshure bahimvye",
      "a_student_who_shows_8_5_as_9_4_because": "Umunyeshure werekana 8 + 5 nka \"9 + 4\" (kubera yafashe 1 kuri 5 akayongera kuri 8 mbere) yahimvye strategy ya make-ten. Igaragaze; uyihe izina; wigishe ishure kuyigerageza. Inzira y'igitabo si yo nzira imwe gusa yukuri.",
      "using_too_many_manipulatives_at_once": "Gukoresha manipulatives nyinshi icarimwe",
      "a_table_covered_in_4_different_manipul": "Ameza yuzuye manipulatives 4 zitandukanye ni inzira yo gukwirakwiza ubwenge, si differentiation. Toranya IMWE ku isomo rimwe. Izindi 11 muri iki gikoresho ni nziza — ku masomo andi.",
      "forgetting_to_ask_why": "Kwibagirwa kubaza \"kuki?\"",
      "students_will_arrange_counters_correct": "Abanyeshure bazategura counters neza kubera bibuka intambwe, batasobanukiwe ico bisigura. \"Kuki washize 1 mu column ya icumi?\" bigomba kuba ikibazo cawe ubaza cane.",
      "cleaning_up_too_quickly": "Gukuraho vuba cane",
      "a_built_construction_is_a_powerful_art": "Inyubako yubatswe ni ikintu gikomeye — uyisige ku ameza mu gihe ishure ririkiganiraho. Yibike muri Isomero nimba uyikeneye ejo. Ntutume abanyeshure basenya inyubako bagize ingorane bubaka kugira ngo \"biteguye isomo rikurikira.\"",
      "asking_only_convergent_questions": "Kubaza ibibazo vya convergent gusa",
      "what_is_4_3_has_one_answer_convergent_": "\"Ni iki 4 + 3?\" gifite igisubizo kimwe (convergent). \"Nyereka 7 mu buryo butatu butandukanye\" gifite vyinshi (divergent). Prompts za divergent zigaragaza uko abanyeshure biyumvira — ari yo assessment y'ingenzi.",
      "about_math_manipulatives": "Ku Bikoresho vy'Imibare",
      "a_virtual_kit_of_12_classic_k_5_math_m": "Kit ya virtual ya manipulatives 12 gakondo z'imibare za K-5, hamwe na scaffold ya CRA progression, ",
      "a_challenge_bank_a_ccss_standards_brow": "banki y'ibibazo, CCSS standards browser, isomero ry'amakarita y'ibikorwa ashobora gucapwa, na ",
      "a_teacher_dashboard_with_progress_expo": "dashboard y'umwigisha ifite gusohora iterambere.",
      "built_as_part_of": "Yubatswe nk'igice ca ",
      "an_open_source_learning_platform_for_k": ", urubuga rwo kwiga rwa open-source ku mashure ya K-12. ",
      "alloflow_is_licensed_under_agpl_v3": "AlloFlow ifite uruhusha munsi ya AGPL v3.",
      "sources_credits": "Amasoko & gushimira",
      "pedagogy_bruner_1966_witzel_mercer_mil": "Uburezi: Bruner (1966), Witzel/Mercer/Miller (meta-analysis 2003), Carbonneau/Marley/Selig (meta-analysis 2013).",
      "manipulatives_montessori_golden_beads_": "Manipulatives: Montessori (Golden Beads), Cuisenaire (1952), Gattegno (Geoboard), Singapore Math (Number Bonds).",
      "standards_common_core_state_standards_": "Standards: Common Core State Standards for Mathematics, K-7.",
      "accessibility_wcag_2_1_aa_okabe_ito_cb": "Accessibility: WCAG 2.1 AA. Palette ya Okabe-Ito nziza ku buhumyi bw'ibara.",
      "audio_web_audio_api_for_sound_effects_": "Audio: Web Audio API ku sound effects, ishobora kuzimwa burundu.",
      "privacy": "Ibanga",
      "all_state_lives_in_your_browser_no_dat": "Imimerere yose ibamo muri browser yawe. Nta data yoherezwa ahantu keretse iyo wowe ubwawe uyisohoye. ",
      "browser_storage_is_per_device_clearing": "Ububiko bwa browser ni ubwa buri gikoresho — gusiba data ya site bisubiramo iterambere.",
      "clear_6": "↺ Siba",
