      "algebra_tiles_make_abstract_algebra_ph": "💡 Algebra tiles zituma abstract algebra iba iy'umubiri. Tile positive na negative y'imiterere imwe zikora \"zero pair.\" Tiles zifite ibara ryuzuye ni positive; tiles zera zifite umupaka wa dashed ni negative. Zikoreshe gukora model ya expressions, korosha, na (ku banyeshure bakuru) factor quadratics uhuza tiles mu rectangles.",
      "select_a_tool_above_to_get_started": "Toranya igikoresho co hejuru kugira ngo utangure."
