      "warm_lo_fi_keys": "Warm lo-fi keys",
      "barry_harris_1929_2021_codified_bebop_": "Barry Harris (1929-2021) yateguye harmony ya bebop mu buryo. Uburyo bwe bukoresha 6th chords aho gukoresha 7ths kandi bwongeraho diminished passing chords hagati y'ivyiciro vya scale kugira ngo ijwi riyoborwe neza.",
      "ii_v_i_jazz": "ii-V-I (Jazz)",
      "12_bar_blues": "12-Bar Blues",
