      "4th_overtone": "Overtone ya 4",
      "5th_overtone": "Overtone ya 5",
      "6th_overtone": "Overtone ya 6",
      "7th_overtone": "Overtone ya 7",
      "attack_time_to_reach_full_volume_decay": "Attack: igihe co kugera kuri volume yuzuye. Decay: igihe co kumanuka kugera sustain. Sustain: urwego rwa volume rubandanya. Release: igihe co kuzima nyuma yo kurekura key.",
      "a_scale_is_an_ordered_set_of_pitches_m": "Scale ni itsinda rya pitches ryateguwe. Modes ni ukuzunguruka kwa scale gutangura ku vyiciro bitandukanye. Buri kimwe gishiraho imyumvire itandukanye.",
      "chords_are_built_by_stacking_intervals": "Chords zubakwa mu gutuma intervals (3rds) zikurikirana. Major ikoresha major 3rd + minor 3rd. Minor irazihindura. Extended chords zongeraho 7ths, 9ths, n'ibirenga.",
      "kicks_use_a_sine_oscillator_with_a_pit": "Kicks zikoresha sine oscillator ifite pitch sweep. Snares zivanga noise (yasukuwe) + tone body. Hi-hats zikoresha high-pass filtered noise bursts.",
      "4_4_4_quarter_note_beats_per_bar_most_": "4/4 = quarter-note beats 4 kuri buri bar (isanzwe cane). 3/4 = imyumvire ya waltz. 6/8 = compound duple. 5/4 na 7/8 bikora grooves zidahwitse, z'amahanga.",
      "keys_arranged_by_ascending_5ths_clockw": "Keys zategujwe na 5ths zizamuka mu cerekezo c'isaha. Keys ziturana zisangira 6 muri 7 z'amanota. Kuja mu cerekezo c'isaha vyongera sharps; mu cerekezo kinyuranye vyongera flats.",
      "every_musical_sound_contains_overtones": "Buri jwi ry'umuziki rifite overtones hejuru ya fundamental. Imbaraga zabo bijanye zigena timbre — ni yo mpamvu trumpet ivuga itandukanye na flute kuri pitch imwe.",
      "an_interval_is_the_distance_between_tw": "Interval ni intera hagati ya pitches ebyiri, ipimwa muri semitones. Frequency ratio igena consonance (ratios zoroshe nka 3:2 zumvikana neza).",
      "plays_chord_notes_one_at_a_time_in_seq": "Ikina amanota ya chord rimwe rimwe mu murongo. Hejuru = kuva hasi kugera hejuru, Hasi = kuva hejuru kugera hasi. Ikora patterns zitemba ziva kuri chords zihamye.",
      "a_filter_removes_frequencies_above_low": "Filter ikuraho frequencies ziri hejuru (lowpass), hasi (highpass), canke hafi (bandpass) ya cutoff frequency. Resonance (Q) yongera frequencies hafi ya cutoff, ikora peak.",
      "tremolo_periodic_volume_changes_amplit": "Tremolo: impinduka za volume z'igihe n'igihe (amplitude modulation). Vibrato: impinduka za pitch z'igihe n'igihe (frequency modulation). Vyombi bigenzurwa na LFO (Low Frequency Oscillator).",
      "discovered_in_1983_a_noise_burst_feeds": "Vyavumbuwe mu 1983. Noise burst yinjira muri delay line ngufi cane ifite feedback. Delay time igena pitch. Filter iri muri feedback loop igenzura urumuri na decay. Isa na plucked strings mu buryo busanzwe.",
      "the_sequencer_is_a_composition_tool_ea": "Sequencer ni igikoresho co guhanga. Buri step igereranya subdivision ya beat. Umurongo wa melody ushiraho pitched notes, drums zongeraho rythme. Musical notation yerekana ivyo ukora.",
      "notes_on_lines_and_spaces_represent_pi": "Amanota ari ku mirongo n'umwanya agereranya pitches. Igihe kigaragazwa n'imiterere y'inota: whole (○), half (𝅗𝅥), quarter (♩), eighth (♪). Staff ifite imirongo 5.",
