      "play_piano_keys_presets": "Kina — piano keys + presets",
      "equal_temperament_12_notes_per_octave_": "Equal temperament: amanota 12 kuri octave, ratio 2^(1/12). A4 = 440 Hz; A5 = 880 Hz. Well-Tempered Clavier ya Bach (1722) yemeje isi kuri iyi masezerano. Buri nota ukina hano iri kuri grid iyo.",
      "scales_the_major_minor_modal_grammar": "Scales — imiterere ya major + minor + modal",
      "major_w_w_h_w_w_w_h_minor_w_h_w_w_h_w_": "Major: W-W-H-W-W-W-H. Minor: W-H-W-W-H-W-W. Modes 7 (Ionian, Dorian, Phrygian, Lydian, Mixolydian, Aeolian, Locrian) ziva mu kuzunguruka interval pattern ya major scale.",
      "chords_stacked_thirds_inversions": "Chords — thirds zateranyijwe + inversions",
      "triads_root_third_fifth_major_4_3_semi": "Triads: root + third + fifth. Major (4+3 semitones), minor (3+4), diminished (3+3), augmented (4+4). 7th chords zongeraho third indi. Umuziki pop = ~chords 6 zisubiramo; jazz ikoresha extensions na substitutions.",
      "harmony_pad_voiced_pads_drones": "Harmony Pad — voiced pads + drones",
      "sustained_chord_textures_the_bed_under": "Sustained chord textures — igitanda kiri munsi ya hafi buri cinematic score. Gerageza iv-V-i muri minor, canke i-VI-VII ku myumvire ya Hans Zimmer. Drones muri fifths zishigikira umuziki gakondo w'Ubuhinde n'imigenzo ya bagpipe.",
      "beat_pad_sample_based_drums": "Beat Pad — sample-based drums",
      "most_popular_music_sits_at_4_4_90_130_": "Umuziki mwinshi uzwi uri kuri 4/4, 90-130 BPM. Hip-hop ~85-95, house 120-130, drum-and-bass ~170 (imyumvire ya half-time). Kick kuri 1+3, snare kuri 2+4 = backbeat — urufatiro rwa rock + pop.",
      "theory_the_math_behind_the_sound": "Theory — imibare iri inyuma y'ijwi",
      "pythagoras_500_bce_discovered_consonan": "Pythagoras (~500 BCE) yavumbuye consonance uva muri integer frequency ratios: octave 2:1, fifth 3:2, fourth 4:3. Helmholtz yavyaguye mu 1862. Ijwi = compression waves; umuziki = patterns twemeye kwita nziza.",
