      "fm_synthesis_2": "FM Synthesis",
      "frequency_modulation_fm_synthesis_uses": "Frequency Modulation (FM) synthesis ikoresha oscillator imwe (modulator) guhindura frequency y'indi (carrier) vuba. Ratio ya modulator:carrier igena harmonic content. Ratios zoroshe (1:1, 2:1, 3:1) zikora harmonic tones. Ratios zigoye zikora metallic, bell-like, canke inharmonic sounds. Yamaha DX7 yamamaje FM mu 1983.",
