      "removes_frequencies_above_lowpass_or_b": "Ikuraho frequencies ziri hejuru (lowpass) canke hasi (highpass) ya threshold. Nko gupfuka umunwa n'ukuboko — frequencies zo hejuru zirazimira, ijwi rihinduka \"ryijimye\" cane.",
      "delay": "Delay",
      "creates_echoes_by_copying_the_signal_a": "Ikora echoes mu gukoporora signal no kuyisubiramo nyuma y'igihe gito. Feedback igenzura umubare wa echoes zisubiramo.",
      "reverb_2": "Reverb",
      "simulates_room_acoustics_by_creating_t": "Isa na acoustics y'icumba mu gukora echoes ntoya ibihumbi zivanga. Icumba gito = reverb ngufi, katedrali = reverb ndende.",
      "distortion": "Distortion",
      "clips_the_waveform_peaks_turning_smoot": "Ikata peaks za waveform, ihindura sine waves zoroheje mu miterere ikomeye, ifite inguni. Ibi vyongeraho harmonics nshasha zitari mu ijwi ry'umwimerere.",
      "chorus": "Chorus",
      "duplicates_the_signal_with_a_slight_co": "Ikoporora signal na delay ntoya ihinduka buri gihe. Ibi bisa na voices/ibikoresho vyinshi bikina hamwe bidahuye gato.",
      "tremolo": "Tremolo",
      "rapidly_varies_the_volume_up_and_down_": "Ihindura volume hejuru na hasi vuba, ikora effet itera. Isanzwe muri guitar surf n'umuziki wa organ.",
      "use_headphones_when_monitoring_to_avoi": "Koresha headphones mu gihe co kumonitoringa kugira ngo wirinde feedback loops! Mic inyura muri effects zose zo hejuru (filter, delay, reverb, n'ibindi) — zigenge kugira ngo wumve uko buri imwe ihindura ijwi canke igikoresho cawe.",
      "connect_your_microphone_to_run_your_vo": "Huza microphone yawe kugira ngo ijwi canke igikoresho cawe kinyure muri effects chain ako kanya.",
      "see_your_voice_as_a_waveform_frequency": "Raba ijwi ryawe nka waveform + frequency spectrum. Umva uko filter, delay, reverb, distortion, na chorus bihindura sound waves mu buryo bw'umubiri.",
