      "xy_pad_performance": "XY Pad Performance",
      "the_xy_pad_maps_your_finger_mouse_posi": "XY pad ishira ahantu h'urutoki/imbeba yawe ku musical parameters ako kanya. X axis igenzura pitch (ibumoso = hasi, iburyo = hejuru). Y axis igenzura filter cutoff frequency (hejuru = urumuri, hasi = ryijimye). Ibi bisa n'ibikoresho nka Korg Kaoss Pad, cahinduye live electronic music performance mu guhindura 2D gestures mu ijwi.",
      "xy_performance_pad_left_right_is_pitch": "XY performance pad. Ibumoso–iburyo ni pitch, hejuru–hasi ni filter brightness. Koresha arrow keys kugira ngo ugende ukine nota; fyonda Escape canke Space kugira ngo uhagarare.",
