      "tiny_magnetic_field_from_partially_mol": "Umurima muto wa magneti uva ku ntima yashonze igice. Ntuhagije kurinda ubuso.",
      "no_global_magnetic_field_solar_wind_in": "Nta murima wa magneti w'umubumbe wose. Umuyaga w'izuba uhurira n'ikirere ako kanya.",
      "strong_dipole_field_from_liquid_iron_o": "Umurima ukomeye wa dipole uva ku ntima yo hanze y'icuma c'amazi. Ukora imikandara ya Van Allen. Ni ingenzi ku buzima!",
      "lost_its_global_field_4_billion_years_": "Wabuze umurima wawo w'umubumbe wose mu myaka ~miliyari 4 ishize. Magnetisimu isigaye mu gishishwa ca kera.",
      "strongest_in_solar_system_deadly_radia": "Ukomeye kurusha iyindi muri sisitemu y'izuba! Imikandara y'imirasire yica. Hidorojene ya metali ikora uwo murima.",
      "unique_almost_perfectly_aligned_with_r": "Udasanzwe: uhuye hafi neza n'umurongo wo kuzenguruka. Intima ya hidorojene ya metali.",
      "tilted_59_from_rotation_axis_off_cente": "Wanamye 59° uvuye ku murongo wo kuzenguruka! Nturi hagati. Imiterere idasanzwe cane.",
      "also_highly_tilted_47_and_off_center_c": "Nawo wanamye cane (47°) kandi nturi hagati. Ibidukikije vya magneti bigoye.",
      "too_small_and_cold_for_a_dynamo_no_pro": "Muto kandi ukonje cane ku buryo hataba dinamo. Nta kirinda umuyaga w'izuba.",
      "venus_has_a_runaway_greenhouse_effect_": "Venus ifite ingaruka z'inzu y'ibimera zidashobora guhagarara zigera kuri 462°C!",
      "saturn_has_146_known_moons_as_of_2024": "Saturn ifite amezi 293 azwi ku rutonde rwa JPL rw'amasatelite y'imibumbe rw'ubu.",
      "uranus_has_an_axial_tilt_of_97_77": "Uranus yanamye ku murongo wayo ku rugero rwa 97.77°!",
      "mercury_is_only_4_879_km_in_diameter": "Mercury ifite umurambararo wa km 4,879 gusa.",
      "pluto_takes_248_earth_years_to_orbit_t": "Pluto ifata imyaka 248 y'Isi kugira ngo izenguruke Izuba!",
      "jupiter_rotates_in_just_10_hours": "Jupiter izenguruka mu masaha 10 gusa!",
      "iron_oxide_rust_gives_mars_its_red_col": "Okiside y'icuma (ingese) ni yo iha Mars ibara ryayo ritukura.",
      "saturn_s_density_is_less_than_water_0_": "Ubwinshi bwa Saturn buri munsi y'ubw'amazi (0.687 g/cm³)!",
      "olympus_mons_on_mars_is_21_9_km_high_n": "Olympus Mons kuri Mars ifite uburabure bwa km 21.9 — hafi inshuro 3 za Everest!",
      "neptune_s_winds_reach_2_100_km_h": "Imiyaga ya Neptune igera kuri 2,100 km/h!",
      "earth_s_magnetic_field_deflects_charge": "Umurima wa magneti w'Isi wirukana uduce dufite amashanyarazi duva ku zuba. Ozone ifasha kuri UV, ariko magnetosifeeri ni yo ngabo y'ibanze!",
      "the_iau_s_2006_definition_requires_pla": "Ibisobanuro vya IAU vyo mu 2006 bisaba ko imibumbe isukura inzira yayo y'orbite ikayivanamo ibindi bisigazwa.",
      "also_called_the_goldilocks_zone_not_to": "Nanone hitwa « agace ka Goldilocks » — ntigashuha cane, ntigakonja cane, ku buryo amazi adakonje yabaho ku buso.",
      "the_moon_rotates_exactly_once_per_orbi": "Ukwezi kuzenguruka rimwe gusa kuri buri rugendo — uku guhuza guterwa n'imbaraga z'imiraba mu myaka miliyari.",
      "opportunity_rover_found_hematite_blueb": "Rover Opportunity yabonye « uduterekurutsi » twa hematite — amabuye ashobora gukorwa gusa mu mazi. Amafoto yo mu kirere yerekana inkengero za kera z'imigezi!",
      "venus_is_hotter_462_c_vs_430_c_mercury": "Venus irushushe (462°C kuri 430°C)! Mercury nta kirere ifite co gufata ubushuhe. Ingaruka z'inzu y'ibimera ni zo zibanza kuruta intera.",
      "gas_giants_have_no_solid_surface_they_": "Ibihangange vya gaze nta buso bukomeye bifite! Ni gaze ya hidorojene na heliyumu ahanini igenda ikomera uko wegera intima. Sonde yamanuka itagira aho igarukira.",
      "earth_s_distance_from_the_sun_doesn_t_": "Intera y'Isi n'Izuba ntihinduka ku munsi. Saa sita bivuze gusa ko Izuba riri hejuru cane mu kirere cawe. Isi iba hafi cane muri Nzero (perihelion)!",
      "jupiter_is_11x_wider_than_earth_and_1_": "Jupiter iragutse inshuro 11 kurusha Isi, kandi Isi 1,300 zashoboraga kwinjira muri yo! Sisitemu y'izuba ifite itandukaniro rikabije ry'ubunini.",
      "pluto_is_still_in_the_solar_system_it_": "Pluto iracari muri sisitemu y'izuba! Yavanywe ku « mubumbe » ishirwa ku « mubumbe muto » mu 2006, ariko iracazenguruka Izuba.",
      "the_asteroid_belt_is_mostly_empty_spac": "Umukandara wa asteroyide ahanini ni ubusa! Intera iri hagati ya asteroyide ni miliyoni za km. Ivyogajuru binyuramo nta kaga.",
      "not_always_saturn_is_95x_earth_s_mass_": "Si buri gihe! Saturn ifite misa inshuro 95 y'Isi ariko rukuruzi ku buso ni 1.06g gusa kuko ari nini kandi ifite ubwinshi buke. Ibiro biterwa na misa NA rayo.",
      "all_parts_of_the_moon_receive_sunlight": "Ibice vyose vy'Ukwezi bibona urumuri rw'izuba! « Uruhande rwa kure » ni igice tudashobora kubona tuvuye ku Isi kubera gufatwa n'imiraba. Kibona Izuba nk'ibindi.",
      "the_habitable_zone": "Agace Gatuwe",
      "the_habitable_zone_or_goldilocks_zone_": "Agace gatuwe (canke « agace ka Goldilocks ») ni urwego rw'intera uvuye ku nyenyeri aho amazi adakonje yashobora kubaho ku buso bw'umubumbe. Muri sisitemu yacu y'izuba, Venus iri ku mpera yo imbere, Isi iri hagati, na Mars iri ku mpera yo hanze. Ariko kugira amazi adakonje binasaba ikirere n'umurima wa magneti bikwiye!",
      "the_greenhouse_effect": "Ingaruka z'Inzu y'Ibimera",
      "when_sunlight_heats_a_planet_s_surface": "Iyo urumuri rw'izuba rushusha ubuso bw'umubumbe, ubuso busohora ubushuhe (infarageru). Gaze z'inzu y'ibimera (CO₂, CH₄, H₂O) zifata ubwo bushuhe zikongera kubusohora, bigashusha umubumbe. Inzu y'ibimera y'Isi ni +33°C (itunga ubuzima). Iya Venus ni +510°C (idashobora guhagarara). Mars ntayigira na gato (-60°C ku mpuzandengo). Ingano ya gaze y'inzu y'ibimera ni yo igena icavamo!",
      "magnetic_shields": "Ingabo za Magneti",
      "a_planet_s_magnetic_field_creates_a_ma": "Umurima wa magneti w'umubumbe ukora « magnetosifeeri » — ingabo itagaragara yirukana umuyaga w'izuba (uduce dufite amashanyarazi duva ku Zuba). Magnetosifeeri y'Isi irinda ikirere cacu kandi ituma ubuzima bushoboka. Mars yabuze umurima wayo wa magneti mu myaka miliyari 4 ishize, maze ikirere cayo kigenda kivanwaho buhoro. Magnetosifeeri ya Jupiter ikomeye inshuro 20,000 kurusha iy'Isi!",
      "why_isn_t_pluto_a_planet": "Kuki Pluto atari Umubumbe?",
      "in_2006_the_international_astronomical": "Mu 2006, Ihuriro Mpuzamahanga ry'Ubumenyi bw'Ikirere ryashizeho ibipimo bitatu vy'umubumbe: (1) Uzenguruka Izuba ✓, (2) Ufite misa ihagije yo kugira imiterere y'uruziga ✓, (3) « Wasukuye orbite yawo » uvanamo ibindi bisigazwa ✗. Pluto isangira agace kayo k'orbite n'ibihumbi vy'ibintu vyo mu Mukandara wa Kuiper, bityo ishirwa mu « mibumbe mito ». Ivyo ntibituma iba idashimishije — New Horizons yerekanye ko ikora mu buryo bwa geologiya!",
      "tidal_locking": "Gufatwa n'Imiraba",
      "over_billions_of_years_gravitational_t": "Mu myaka miliyari, imbaraga za rukuruzi z'imiraba zishobora kugabanya umuvuduko wo kuzenguruka kw'ukwezi kugeza kuhuye n'igihe cako co kuzenguruka. Icavuyemo: uruhande rumwe ruhora rwerekeye ku mubumbe. Ukwezi kwacu gufashwe n'imiraba y'Isi. Mercury ifashwe igice n'Izuba (igipimo 3:2). Pluto na Charon bafatanye — bahora bereka uruhande rumwe!",
      "searching_for_life": "Gushaka ubuzima",
      "a_biosignature_is_any_evidence_of_past": "Ikimenyetso c'ubuzima ni ikintu cose kigaragaza ubuzima bwa kera canke ubw'ubu. Abahanga barondera: (1) amazi adakonje, (2) molekile ngugu, (3) gaze zo mu kirere nka ogisijene canke metani zitari kubaho ubuzima butazikoze, (4) inkomoko z'ingufu. Ahantu heza kurusha ahandi muri sisitemu yacu y'izuba: Mars (amazi ya kera), Europa (inyanja iri munsi y'ubuso), Enceladus (amasoko y'amazi), na Titan (ibiyaga vya metani).",
