      "does_eccentricity_change_orbital_perio": "Ese eksantirisite ihindura IGIHE c'orbite? Gerageza e=0 na e=0.5 kuri a imwe.",
      "halley_s_comet_has_a_17_8_au_e_0_97_wh": "Inyenyeri y'umurizo ya Halley ifite a=17.8 AU, e=0.97. Ivyo bisigura iki ku gihe cayo — n'inshuro isura perihelion?",
