      "at_what_e_value_does_an_orbit_become_u": "Ni kuri e ingana ite orbite iva mu gufatwa? Ni iki kigena uwo mupaka?",
      "i_can_explain_why_this_a_e_m_combinati": "Nshobora gusigura impamvu iri huriro rya a/e/M ritanga ubu bwoko bw'orbite.",
      "explain_in_your_own_words": "Sigura mu magambo yawe...",
      "inquiry_widget_no_score_no_reveal_no_a": "Igikoresho c'ubushakashatsi — nta manota, nta gisubizo cerekanwa, nta bisubizo bisukwa. T = √(a³/M) nk'uko Kepler III abivuga, M mu misa z'izuba, a muri AU, T mu myaka. Vis-viva ikoreshwa kuri v kuri perihelion / aphelion.",
      "full_orrery_animated_solar_system": "Orrery yuzuye — sisitemu y'izuba igenda",
      "all_8_planets_to_scale_size_orbit_watc": "Imibumbe 8 yose ku gipimo (ubunini + orbite). Raba Mercury izenguruka Izuba inshuro ~4 ku mwaka w'Isi. Imibumbe yo imbere yegeranye; iyo hanze ifite ama orbite manini.",
      "kepler_i_orbits_are_ellipses": "Kepler I — ama orbite ni ama elipsi",
      "every_planet_orbits_in_an_ellipse_with": "Buri mubumbe uzenguruka mu elipsi, Izuba riri ku kibanza kimwe. Ikindi kibanza ni ubusa. Orbite y'Isi ifite eksantirisite nkeya cane (e ≈ 0.017).",
      "kepler_ii_equal_areas_in_equal_times": "Kepler II — ubuso bungana mu gihe kingana",
      "a_line_from_planet_to_sun_sweeps_equal": "Umurongo uva ku mubumbe uja ku Zuba upfukirana ubuso bungana mu gihe kingana — bivuze ko imibumbe igenda VUBA iri hafi y'Izuba (perihelion) kandi BUHORO iri kure (aphelion).",
      "kepler_iii_period_semi_major_axis": "Kepler III — igihe² ∝ umurongo-munini-wa-hagati³",
      "t_a_when_t_is_in_years_and_a_is_in_au_": "T² = a³ iyo T iri mu myaka na a iri muri AU. Isi ifite T=1, a=1 bituma imibare iba itomoye neza. Kwikuba kabiri ubunini bw'orbite bikuba igihe ~2.83.",
      "workshop_build_your_own_orbit": "Uruganda — wubake orbite yawe",
      "set_semi_major_axis_eccentricity_the_o": "Shiraho umurongo munini wa hagati + eksantirisite; orrery yerekana orbite ako kanya. Gerageza e=0.9 — ubwo ni ubwa nyenyeri z'imirizo. Gerageza e=0 — uruziga rutunganye.",
      "hohmann_transfers_actual_rocket_math": "Ukwimuka kwa Hohmann — imibare nyayo ya roketi",
      "the_minimum_energy_way_to_travel_betwe": "Uburyo bukoresha ingufu nkeya kurusha ubundi bwo kugenda hagati y'ama orbite abiri y'uruziga. Gutwika kabiri: kuva ku orbite yo imbere kuri perihelion y'ukwimuka, kugera ku orbite yo hanze kuri aphelion.",
      "challenges_apply_kepler_s_laws": "Ibibazo — koresha amategeko ya Kepler",
      "multi_step_problems_predict_periods_fr": "Ibibazo vy'intambwe nyinshi: hanura ibihe uhereye ku murongo munini wa hagati, menya umuvuduko wa perihelion ugereranyije n'uwa aphelion, bara Δv y'orbite y'ukwimuka. Ni urwego rwa AP Physics 1 + 2.",
      "true_false_concept_check": "Ukuri / Ikinyoma — raba iciyumviro",
      "quick_discrimination_quiz_on_common_ke": "Ikizamini cihuse co gutandukanya ivyiyumviro bibi bikunze kubaho kuri Kepler. Kigamije imigani y'orbite (« hafi = buhoro », « ama orbite ni uruziga », « ama orbite yose agana ikerekezo kimwe »).",
