      "36_500_objects_orbit_earth_at_various_": "Ibintu 36,500 bizenguruka Isi ku burabure butandukanye. Nyuza umurongo w'uburabure urabe ibihari.",
      "altitude_3": "Uburabure hejuru",
      "36_500_tracked_objects_millions_of_fra": "Ibintu 36,500 bikurikiranwa + miliyoni z'ibice bizenguruka Isi. Akaga ka Kessler Syndrome: urukurikirane rwo kugongana rutuma ikirere kitakoreshwa. SpaceX Starlink ifite ivyogajuru 5000+; iteganya ibindi vyinshi.",
