      "cosmic_speeds_chart": "⚡ Imbonerahamwe y'Imivuduko y'Isanzure",
      "from_walking_to_light_speed_log_scale_": "Kuva ku kugenda n'amaguru kugeza ku muvuduko w'urumuri (igipimo ca log). Voyager 1 ni co kintu cakozwe n'abantu kiri kure kurusha ibindi kandi ni kimwe mu vyogajuru vyacu vyihuta bigana hanze, ariko kiracagenda buhoro cane ugereranyije n'isanzure.",
      "voyager_1_is_the_fastest_object_humans": "Voyager 1 yihuta ugereranyije n'ibindi vyogajuru kandi ubu ni co kintu cakozwe n'abantu kiri kure kurusha ibindi, nyamara cakenera imyaka ~80,000 ngo kigere ku nyenyeri iri hafi kurusha izindi. Urumuri rukora urwo rugendo mu myaka 4.",
