      "10_things_you_can_spot_tonight_with_ju": "Ibintu 10 ushobora kubona muri iri joro ukoresheje amaso yawe gusa canke binokuli.",
      "best_naked_eye_observing_dark_site_awa": "Kuraba neza n'amaso yera: ahantu h'umwijima (kure y'amatara y'umuji), Ukwezi kuri munsi y'aho ijisho rigarukira, amaso yamenyereye umwijima (iminota 20-30 mu mwijima). Za porogaramu z'ubuntu: Stellarium, SkyView, Star Walk zifasha kumenya ico urimo kuraba.",
      "pale_blue_dot": "🌍 Akadomo Kororoheje k'Ubururu",
      "carl_sagan_s_most_quoted_reflection_a_": "Ivyiyumviro vya Carl Sagan bikunze kuvugwa kurusha ibindi. Pikiseli imwe irimwo buri wese twigeze kumenya.",
      "the_pale_blue_dot": "Akadomo Kororoheje k'Ubururu",
      "from_this_distant_vantage_point_the_ea": "« Uhereye kuri iyi ntera ya kure, Isi ishobora kuba isa n'aho itagira ico imaze. Ariko kuri twe, ni ukundi. Ongera urabe ako kadomo. Ni hano. Ni iwacu. Ni twe. Kuri ko, buri wese ukunda, buri wese uzi, buri wese wigeze kumva bavuga, buri muntu wese wabayeho, yamaze ubuzima bwe. »",
      "carl_sagan_pale_blue_dot_1994": "— Carl Sagan, Pale Blue Dot (1994)",
      "voyager_1_took_this_photo_of_earth_fro": "Voyager 1 yafashe iyi foto y'Isi iri mu ntera ya km miliyari 6 ku ya 14 Ruhuhuma 1990 — vyasabwe na Carl Sagan. Isi ni pikiseli imwe. Buri muntu wese mu mateka yabayeho kuri iyo pikiseli.",
