      "dark_site": "Ahantu h'umwijima",
      "drive_30_min_from_city_lights_maine_is": "Genda iminota 30+ mu modoka kure y'amatara y'umuji. Maine yuzuye ahantu nk'aho. Katahdin Woods and Waters ni ahantu hemewe h'ikirere c'umwijima.",
      "most_important_tool_dark_sky_light_pol": "Igikoresho c'ingenzi kurusha ibindi: ikirere c'umwijima. Umwanda w'urumuri usibanganya 90% vy'inyenyeri. Katahdin Woods and Waters NM na AMC Maine Woods ni ahantu hemewe ku rwego mpuzamahanga h'ikirere c'umwijima; Acadia na Baxter na ho hatanga ikirere c'umwijima ciza cane.",
      "how_stars_die": "⚱ Uko Inyenyeri Zipfa",
      "star_s_fate_depends_on_mass_brown_dwar": "Iherezo ry'inyenyeri riterwa na misa yayo: ingufi y'ikigina, ingufi yera, inyenyeri ya neutron, canke umwobo w'umukara.",
      "how_a_star_dies_depends_almost_entirel": "Uko inyenyeri ipfa biterwa hafi ya vyose na misa yayo y'ibanze. Umupaka uri hagati y'inyenyeri ya neutron n'umwobo w'umukara ntuzwi neza (umupaka wa Tolman-Oppenheimer-Volkoff ~2-3 M☉ ku gisigaye).",
      "cosmic_distance_reference": "📏 Icerekezo c'Intera z'Isanzure",
      "from_1km_to_93_billion_light_years_ref": "Kuva kuri km 1 kugeza ku myaka-rumuri miliyari 93. Imbonerahamwe y'ibipimo vy'isanzure.",
      "distances_jump_in_scale_km_to_au_to_ly": "Intera zisimburana ku bipimo: km kuri AU kuri myaka-rumuri kuri miliyari z'imyaka-rumuri. Buri ntambwe ni ~inshuro 10,000-100,000 nini kurushaho. Ubumenyi bw'ikirere bubaho ku gipimo ca log.",
      "maine_night_sky_by_season": "🌲 Ikirere ca Nijoro ca Maine ku Bihe vy'Umwaka",
      "maine_has_world_class_dark_skies_what_": "Maine ifite ikirere c'umwijima ciza ku rwego mpuzamahanga. Ico waraba kuri buri gihe c'umwaka.",
      "maine_has_fantastic_dark_skies_especia": "Maine ifite ikirere c'umwijima ciza cane — cane cane mu majaruguru y'imiji. Katahdin Woods and Waters NM na AMC Maine Woods ni ahantu hemewe ku rwego mpuzamahanga h'ikirere c'umwijima; Acadia, Allagash, Baxter, na Cobscook na ho ni h'umwijima mwiza. Amajoro y'itumba ni maremare + asobanutse neza.",
      "space_news_timeline": "📰 Urutonde rw'Igihe rw'Amakuru y'Ikirere",
      "major_space_missions_events_2024_2027_": "Ubutumwa bukomeye bw'ikirere + ivyabaye 2024-2027. Turi mu bihe bishimishije.",
      "space_exploration_is_in_a_renaissance_": "Ubushakashatsi bw'ikirere buri mu ivugururwa rikomeye. Ibihugu bishasha (Ubuhinde, Ubuyapani, UAE), amasosiyete mashasha y'abikorera (SpaceX, Blue Origin), ubutumwa bushasha (Europa Clipper, Artemis, JWST). Raba hejuru — kandi utege amatwi.",
      "solar_system_at_a_glance": "📊 Sisitemu y'Izuba mu Ncamake",
      "quick_reference_summary_of_solar_syste": "Incamake yihuse y'ibiri muri sisitemu y'izuba + uko misa igabanijwe.",
      "solar_system_stats": "Imibare ya Sisitemu y'Izuba",
      "the_sun_contains_99_86_of_all_solar_sy": "Izuba rifite 99.86% vya misa yose ya sisitemu y'izuba. Jupiter ifite bibiri vya gatatu vya 0.14% isigaye. Isi + ibindi vyose ni ibisigaye.",
