      "why_we_use_utc": "Impamvu dukoresha UTC",
      "utc_coordinated_universal_time_is_the_": "UTC (Igihe Mpuzamahanga Gihuriweho) ni co gipimo c'isi yose. Gishingiye ku masaha ya atomike.",
      "astronomers_report_events_in_utc_so_ob": "Abahanga b'ikirere batangaza ivyabaye muri UTC kugira ngo ibigo vyo ku isi hose bishobore kugereranya. SpaceX yohereza muri UTC. Ubutumwa bwa NASA buri muri UTC.",
      "maine_utc_5_est_or_utc_4_edt_london_ut": "Maine: UTC-5 (EST) canke UTC-4 (EDT). Londres: UTC+0 (GMT) canke UTC+1 (BST). Ubuyapani: UTC+9.",
      "tip_when_you_read_an_astronomy_event_t": "Impanuro: iyo usomye gahunda y'ibihe vy'ibikorwa vy'ubumenyi bw'ikirere, buri gihe raba nimba iri muri UTC canke mu gihe c'aho uri.",
      "utc_replaced_gmt_in_1972_based_on_atom": "UTC yasimbuye GMT mu 1972. Ishingiye ku masaha ya atomike y'ibigo vy'igihugu ku isi hose, hafashwe impuzandengo. Amasegonda yiyongera ashirwaho igihe bikenewe.",
