      "hue_0_360_around_the_wheel_saturation_": "Hue (0-360 hakurikijwe uruziga), saturation (isuku), urumuri. Ayuzuzanya arahanganye, ay'urumuri rumwe ari hafi, atatu ari ku ntera ya 120°. Newton yashize amabara yose ku ruziga mu 1666.",
