      "paint_and_print_subtractive_cmy_mixes_": "Amarangi no gucapa = gukuramwo (CMY iyavanze itanga umwijima); urumuri n'ecran = kongeramwo (RGB iyavanze itanga umweru). Isi imwe, mugabo imibare itandukanye rwose — imashini icapa yiyumvira ku mbaho za K, televiziyo ikatekereza kuri Hz.",
      "pixel_art_bitmap_craft_at_8_8_to_32_32": "Ubuhanzi bwa Pixel — umwuga wa bitmap kuva 8×8 kugeza 32×32",
      "each_pixel_is_a_deliberate_decision_ne": "Buri pixel ni icemezo cafashwe ku bushake. Sprites za NES zizwiho gushira intwari muri 16×16 hakoreshejwe amabara ane gusa. Algorithm y'umurongo ya Bresenham ishushanya imirongo iruhande nta mibare y'ibice.",
