      "bilateral_mirror_rotational_n_fold_poi": "Bw'impande zombi (indorerwamo), bwo kuzenguruka (incuro n), bw'akadomo. Amatsinda 17 y'ibishushanyo vy'urukuta agena buri gishushanyo ca 2D cisubiramo — umurimo wose wa Escher.",
      "spirograph_hypotrochoid_roulettes": "Spirograph — imirongo igoramye ya hypotrochoid",
      "a_small_circle_rolls_inside_a_big_one_": "Uruziga ruto ruzengurukira mu runini, ikaramu ikaba iri kure y'ikigo. Igipimo c'imirongo yombi kigena umubare w'ibibabi; intera ikagena ubugari. Iki gikinisho cahawe uburenganzira mu 1965, mugabo imibare yaco ikomoka mu myaka ya 1700.",
      "generative_algorithm_randomness_as_art": "Iremwa — algorithm + amahirwe nk'umuhanzi",
      "sol_lewitt_wrote_instructions_the_wall": "Sol LeWitt yanditse amabwiriza; uwakoze ku rukuta ni we washize mu bikorwa. Uyu munsi: Processing, p5.js, Cinder. “Umuhanzi ni itegeko, si inyishu.”",
      "spin_art_centripetal_physics_in_paint": "Ubuhanzi bwo Kuzunguruka — fiziki y'imbaraga zikurura ku kigo mu marangi",
      "drop_paint_spin_watch_it_fling_outward": "Ta amarangi, zunguruka, uraba uko ajugunywa hanze mu buryo bw'umuzingi. Damien Hirst yinjije miriyoni acuruza amashusho yo kuzunguruka. Ni fiziki imwe n'iy'imashini yumutsa saladi; F = mω²r.",
      "string_art_curves_from_straight_lines": "Ubuhanzi bw'Umugozi — imirongo igoramye ivuye ku mirongo igororotse",
      "connect_every_n_th_nail_an_envelope_cu": "Huza buri musumari wa n; umurongo w'ibahasha uzagaragara. Mary Everest Boole yabimenyekanishije nk'imibare yo mu ishure hafi y'umwaka wa 1900. Cardioid yakozwe n'imirongo igororotse iracashimisha.",
      "op_art_fooling_the_visual_system": "Op Art — kuriganya sisitemu yo kuraba",
      "bridget_riley_s_moir_fields_vasarely_s": "Imirima ya moiré ya Bridget Riley, urusobe rwa Vasarely. Utugingo tw'impera tw'ubwonko dutahura imigendere durenza urugero iyo itandukaniro rihinduka vuba — urupapuro rukagaragara nk'aho *runyeganyega*.",
      "tessellation_the_17_wallpaper_groups": "Amakaro — amatsinda 17 y'ibishushanyo vy'urukuta",
      "every_periodic_2d_tiling_fits_one_of_1": "Buri gishushanyo c'amakaro ca 2D cisubiramo kija mu rimwe mu matsinda 17 y'ubunganya. Escher yabimenye ubwo yasuraga Alhambra mu 1936; hanyuma amara imyaka 30 arangiza urutonde rwose.",
      "fractal_self_similar_at_every_scale": "Fractal — yisusa ku rwego rwose",
      "mandelbrot_1975_cauliflower_coastlines": "Mandelbrot 1975. Shufureri, inkombe z'inyanja, imitsi y'amaraso, inkuba, uduseke tw'umwuka mu bihaha — vyose ni fractal. “Ibicu si imipira, imisozi si za konu, kandi ibishishwa vy'ibiti ntivyoroshe.”",
      "gradient_smooth_color_transitions": "Gradient — ihinduka ry'amabara ryoroshe",
      "css_gives_you_linear_radial_and_conic_": "CSS iguha gradient y'umurongo, iy'uruziga, n'iya conic. Umukororomvya nyawo ufite amabara abandanya (nta mirongo itandukanye) — “amabara 7 y'umukororomvya” yari ugutoranya kwa Newton ku bw'impamvu z'umuziki.",
      "stereogram_3d_from_a_flat_page": "Stereogram — 3D iva ku rupapuro ruringaniye",
      "90s_magic_eye_craze_each_eye_sees_a_sl": "Ubushake bukabije bwa Magic Eye bwo mu myaka ya 90. Buri jisho ribona ishusho yahindutse gato; nurambika canke ugatandukanya amaso yawe neza, ubwonko bwawe buzabihuza bikavyara ubwimbike. Hafi 5% vy'abantu ntibashobora rwose — si amakosa yabo.",
      "contrast_wcag_4_5_1_3_1_apca": "Itandukaniro — WCAG 4.5:1 / 3:1 / APCA",
      "wcag_2_1_normal_text_4_5_1_large_3_1_w": "WCAG 2.1: inyandiko isanzwe 4.5:1, inini 3:1. Impamvu itandukaniro rito ribabaza abasoma badashobora kuraba neza, n'ubwo wowe waba ushobora kurisoma. APCA (isimbura WCAG 3.0) ikoresha urumuri rw'uko ijisho rubona, si igipimo c'urumuri gusa.",
      "harmony_lab_title": "Ubwumvikane - ijwi, igipimo, n'ibara",
      "harmony_lab_hint": "Gereranya intera z'amajwi yumvikana n'atumvikana, huza igipimo c'inshuro n'igishushanyo, kandi uhindure isano y'umuziki mu bwumvikane bw'amaso.",
