      "adjust_base_hue_saturation_lightness_v": "Hindura hue fatizo, saturation, itandukaniro ry'urumuri, kuzenguruka, n'ingano y'amabara. Igikoresho kigaragaza amabara yumvikana ako kanya kandi kikayashira mu bwoko bumwe mu bwumvikane 5 butandukanye. Nta manota, nta nyishu kigaragazwa — bandanya uhindure kandi witegereze ni ibihe bivange bitanga ubuhe bwumvikane.",
